skins.desc: Pheeew... Being able to kick back and relax on such a sunny day is just the best! Oh, Commander! If you'd like to come chill with me, I have watermelon and cold drinks!

skins.name: Bataan
skins.desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Bataan, Hull Number CVL-29.

skins.name: Comfy Cotton Jammies
skins.desc: Yaaaaawn... Huh!? Commander!? You scared me... I was just going to lie down and... Um, yes, with little Hellcat here... Goodnight...

skins.name: Shangri-La
skins.desc: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Shangri-La, Hull Number CV-38.

skins.name: Utopia's Collector
skins.desc: Commander, welcome to my "Utopia." Here, you can find my prized collection. Now, where should we start our detailed tour?

skins.name: Explorer of the Lost World
skins.desc: This specimen looks to be fairly ancient... You could watch from behind me, or you could join me for an up-close examination; we can enjoy our time here however you wish.

skins.name: Little Enterprise
skins.desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier – Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6.

skins.name: Dace
skins.desc: Gato-class submarine - Dace (SS-247)

skins.name: Albacore
skins.desc: Gato-class submarine – Albacore, Hull Number SS-218.

skins.name: Beneath the Black Dress
skins.desc: Oopsie! I totally just dropped something by mistake~! I'd better pick it up quick! Hmm? Saw something you shouldn't have, Commander? Hehehe~ That makes you my partner in crime now!

skins.name: A Catty Surprise!
skins.desc: Surpriiiise! I was in the box all along! ...Did I really freak you out that much? Heehee~ Here, have this voucher as an apology. Come see me later to use it~♪

skins.name: Cavalla
skins.desc: Gato-class submarine – Cavalla, Hull Number SS-244.

skins.name: Convenience Store Raid!
skins.desc: You're late, Commander! ... What's all this? Heheh, it's loot I got from the stop n' rob's bargain bin! Here, have some bread!

skins.name: Colorful Ceremony
skins.desc: Look at all the cute balloons and flowers, and the delicious food as well! Hehe! Parties are the best!

skins.name: Bluegill
skins.desc: Gato-class submarine – Bluegill, Hull Number SS-242.

skins.name: Up-And-Coming Infielder
skins.desc: Look out for Bluegill's ultra-reliable defense, Intrepid! Hehehe, Commander, stay here and see the results of Bluegill's special training!

skins.name: Albacore μ
skins.desc: Lights! Camera! Albacore! Ahaha, don't worry about it, I'm just getting fired up over here! Oh, did you come up with a better idea? Tell me, tell me~

skins.name: Beneath the Black Dress
skins.desc: Oopsie! I totally just dropped something by mistake~! I'd better pick it up quick! Hmm? Saw something you shouldn't have, Commander? Hehehe~ That makes you my partner in crime now!

skins.name: A Catty Surprise!
skins.desc: Surpriiiise! I was in the box all along! ...Did I really freak you out that much? Heehee~ Here, have this voucher as an apology. Come see me later to use it~♪

skins.name: Archerfish
skins.desc: Balao-class submarine – Archerfish, Hull Number SS-311.

skins.name: Coquettish Bunny
skins.desc: You're our lucky guest today, Commander~ You get a taste of my secret concoction... Excuse me, I meant to say "cocktail!" Relax, it won't do anything weird to you~ Probably. Ahaha~

skins.name: The Devil Next Door
skins.desc: Would you look at that – we're sat next to each other in class. Looking forward to doing some "extracurricular activities" with you this term. Hehehe~

skins.name: Nautilus
skins.desc: Narwhal-class submarine-Nautilus, Hull number SS-168.

skins.name: Afternoon Stretches
skins.desc: Phew~ Standing for a long time really wears you out... Hwah?! Commander, when'd you get there? Um, if you'd like, would you like to come exercise with me?

skins.name: Vestal
skins.desc: Repair ship ー Vestal, Hull Number AR-4!

skins.name: Revigorating Hestia
skins.desc: Listen, everyone~! Playing by the beach is fun, but please keep safety in mind! If you begin to feel ill, come see me~!

skins.name: Seattle
skins.desc: Light cruiser – Seattle.

skins.name: Gorgeous Party
skins.desc: Hey! Great to have you here, Commander! I've gotta ask, whaddya think of my dress? Looking real gorgeous, right? ...Phew, awesome! I was worried my dress didn't look nice and might be dragging down the party mood, that's all!

skins.name: Christmas Party Prep!
skins.desc: Meeeerry Christmas~! Even though the party is about to start, as you can see, I'm still getting ready~ Just gimme a moment, all righty~?

skins.name: Sunfish Spell!
skins.desc: Supportive sorceress Seattle, comin' in hot! So, something got you down, my good pal? I'm up to talk about whatever's on your mind, but in return, you've gotta come to my party tonight!

skins.name: Georgia
skins.desc: Battleship – Georgia.

skins.name: South Town Pearl
skins.desc: Oh? Commander, did you need to get some fresh air as well? Me? Ahaha... It's a bit too stiff inside that venue, so I came out for a change of pace. Why don't we take a little stroll together?

skins.name: Lanier Swan
skins.desc: Heh heh, the warm sun and the sea breeze really hit the spot, don't they? Alright, let's get out there and enjoy ourselves! That's what you've been waiting for, right, Commander?

skins.name: Exalted Vibrance
skins.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I guess you dress up all flashy like this for the Sakura New Year. Would you escort me...? What are you gawking like that for...? Haha, am I so dazzling? Hahaha!

skins.name: Anchorage
skins.desc: Heavy cruiser – Anchorage.

skins.name: Amazon
skins.desc: A-class prototype destoryer ー Amazon, Hull Number D39!

skins.name: Little Orchestra
skins.desc: No ball is complete without its orchestra! Here, as the leader of the Royal Destroyers Philharmonic, I'll be sure to liven up the night! Now to begin... woaaah! I stepped on my mantle?!

skins.name: Amazon (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Selecting me for a retrofit proves that you are a Commander of culture! Heheh, you'd better prepare yourself! From now on, I'll make sure to "take care" of you even more thoroughly!

skins.name: Acasta
skins.desc: A-class destroyer – Acasta, Hull Number H09.

skins.name: Fashionable Outing
skins.desc: Hm? Guess we're both about to head out... Don't stare at me like that... Even I go outdoors sometimes... Since we're both, uh, headed the same way... maybe we could... walk there together?

skins.name: Lights of the Lantern Festival
skins.desc: I heard you're supposed to hang lanterns up everywhere during the Spring Festival... so Ardent and I gave it a try! What do you think? Pretty cute, right? Um... I was talking about the lanterns...

skins.name: Monochromatic Marvel
skins.desc: Come on, stop running around and behave already... Ah, Commander? Umm, I'm currently looking after these rabbits... Hm, you're thirsty? Um, give me a moment and I'll whip something up for you...

skins.name: Acasta (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Ardent told me I "gotta stop looking so tired" and I "gotta be more girly," so I did it while I was retrofitting... Do you recognise me, Commander? ... Umm, I'm Acasta, okay?

skins.name: Ardent
skins.desc: A-class destroyer – Ardent, Hull Number H41.

skins.name: Ardent Valentine
skins.desc: Ehehe~ What do you think, Commander? If you're just going to say "cute," I won't know if you're talking about my school uniform or the chocolate I made...

skins.name: Master Ardent?
skins.desc: Welcome to Ardent's game house~! I'm here to provide fun and excitement for everyone as the GM– ...Ehehe, actually, I'm still learning as a play~♪

skins.name: Ardent (Retrofit)
skins.desc: New outfit, new rigging, same ardent spirit! Ahaha, I'm serious~! Commander, thanks a lot~!

skins.name: Beagle
skins.desc: B-class destroyer ー Beagle, Hull Number H30!

skins.name: Bulldog
skins.desc: B-class destroyer ー Bulldog, Hull Number H91!

skins.name: Comet
skins.desc: C-class destroyer ー Comet, Hull Number H00!

skins.name: Comet (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Do ya reckon... I you think I've become more idol-like? Mhm! As a new idol, I'll show y'all... I'll show you how hard I work as a new idol!

skins.name: Crescent
skins.desc: C-class destroyer ー Crescent, Hull Number H48!

skins.name: Crescent (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Cute? Pretty? Is that all? Can't you expand your vocabulary a little? Jeez... Commander, you really should learn to whisper sweet nothings into my ear!

skins.name: Cygnet
skins.desc: C-class destroyer ー Cygnet, Hull Number H83!

skins.name: Sea Star on Shore
skins.desc: Well, the swimsuit that Hood gave to me is a little tight, don't you think? Want to play beach volleyball? Do you think... can we win?

skins.name: Holy Night's Hymn
skins.desc: H-happy Christmas! A-after that... umm... I have this present for ya, Commander...

skins.name: Winter Date
skins.desc: Aww... it took me a while to get changed... Commander, did I keep you waiting long? Hehe... th-that's good. Let's get going, then~

skins.name: An Offer To Be Maid
skins.desc: M-Master... good evening... C-Commander, don't stare at me so intently... *Whimper*... Saratoga told me that this is part of marketing yourself as an idol...

skins.name: Royal Fanfare
skins.desc: C-Commander? Erm... They picked me to be a cheerleader for the Royal Navy team at the sports thing, so I'm practicin' my cheers... D-don't stare at me like that... I'm shy enough... Already...

skins.name: Cygnet (Retrofit)
skins.desc: This outfit is a little tight... Yes, really? I understand. I've got to work harder for the Royal Navy!

skins.name: Foxhound
skins.desc: F-class destroyer ー Foxhound, Hull Number H69!

skins.name: Foxhound (Retrofit)
skins.desc: I've grown so much that I can't jump like I used to... Commander, are you surprised by my post-retrofit appearance? *Giggle*

skins.name: Fortune
skins.desc: F-class destroyer ー Fortune, Hull Number H70!

skins.name: Seraphic Sunshine
skins.desc: The weather is so nice and sunny, I'm sure whatever I do today will be a success. May everyone else have a good day today as well... Awauh! Little manjuu, are you okay? I can't believe I tripped...

skins.name: Fortune (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Is this really going to help you, Commander? Ah? I doubt our destiny will change with this... Just kidding, Commander! Anything for you.

skins.name: Grenville
skins.desc: G-class Destroyer - Grenville (H03)

skins.name: Glowworm
skins.desc: G-class destroyer ー Glowworm, Hull Number H92!

skins.name: Jokey Adjudicator
skins.desc: Ahahaha! It is I, Glowworm, the impartial and absolute judge! Any wrongdoers will have me to answer to! Guilty verdicts will result in headbutts!

skins.name: Hardy
skins.desc: H-class destroyer – Hardy (H87)

skins.name: Hunter
skins.desc: H-class destroyer – Hunter (H35)

skins.name: Javelin
skins.desc: J-class destroyer ー Javelin, Hull Number F61!

skins.name: Beach Picnic!
skins.desc: Everyone, hurry up! We rarely get to go out to play, so let's make every minute count! Javelin packed plenty of lunches, so let's have a picnic by the beach!

skins.name: Let's Become Waitresses!
skins.desc: Tada! We’re all wearing the same uniform! It’s super cute, isn’t it? Heehee, I’ll be wearing it the entire time I’m on duty, so make sure to visit!

skins.name: Slow Ahead!
skins.desc: Javelin, advancing very slowly! Heehee~♪

skins.name: Operation: Pillow Fight!
skins.desc: Laffey, Z23, Ayanami, and Unicorn - are you girls ready? Ehehe~ I'm not planning to lose to any of you today~!

skins.name: Energetic Idol @120% Motivation!
skins.desc: "Hello, everyone~! I'm Javelin, the new idol who arrived from the Royal Navy! I hope that my songs will be able to bring a smile to everyone's faces, so please take good care of me!" Hehe, how was that for an introduction, Commander?

skins.name: A Legend is Born?!
skins.desc: *pant* *pant*... I finally got it! The legendary hero's... Ah, d-don't worry about it! This thing might look a bit weird, but my ATK stat has indeed gone up!

skins.name: Blissful Purity
skins.desc: Today, I must be the happiest girl in the world! Hehe~

skins.name: Javelin (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Heavy attack mode prepared, ready to use ultimate firepower! Check out the incredible glow on this new gun!

skins.name: Juno
skins.desc: J-class destroyer ー Juno, Hull Number F46!

skins.name: Fairly Flavourful Festival
skins.desc: I love the bustle of a Sakura festival! Commander, care to try some of Akashi's takoyaki? I've heard their taste is out of this world!

skins.name: Vampire
skins.desc: V-class destroyer ー Vampire, Hull Number D68!

skins.name: The Breath of Spring
skins.desc: What do you think of my new outfit? You love it? Or just like it? Haha, your answer is written right on your face. Next... wait, wait, wait! I haven't put my socks on yet!

skins.name: Little Devil in White
skins.desc: Commander, I am now a nurse, so thou hast no choice but to give me thy blood~! Hehe, just kidding~!

skins.name: Night Princess's Regalia
skins.desc: Commander, thou promised to go to the festival with me, right? If thou forgot, I shall have to give thee a nibble upon the neck, ehehe~

skins.name: Night Princess Idol
skins.desc: Feast thine eyes upon Vampire's idol attire... is it not exquisite? Heheh, now thy gaze shall be fixed upon my performance alone~♪

skins.name: Eloi's Blessing
skins.desc: Those who fall in love with vampires are bound to suffer seven times more than their infatuation. After all, love is a poison which leads to death.

skins.name: Jupiter
skins.desc: J-class destroyer – Jupiter, Hull Number F85.

skins.name: Fanclub Sleepover
skins.desc: Good evening, Commander. There's a new show on the telly. You want to watch with me?

skins.name: Jersey
skins.desc: J-class destroyer – Jersey, Hull Number F72!

skins.name: Matchless
skins.desc: M-class destroyer – Matchless (G52.)

skins.name: Escort Me Please!
skins.desc: Ah, Commander, over here! Hm, you're going to take care of all the plans for today's date? In that case, I look forward to seeing just how suave you can be! Hehe~

skins.name: Musketeer
skins.desc: M-class destroyer – Musketeer (G86.)

skins.name: Echo
skins.desc: E-class destroyer – Echo.

skins.name: Eskimo
skins.desc: Eskimo, Tribal-class Destroyer, is here! Oi, this fleet's not half bad! Nice to meet you, Commander!

skins.name: Parkaless Prankster
skins.desc: Oh woe, nobody wants to play with me because they're all too busy~ ...Oh, hello little Manjuu... Heheh, maybe I'll play a prank on you instead!

skins.name: Icarus
skins.desc: I-class destroyer – Icarus.

skins.name: One-Week Medical Experience?
skins.desc: This is a special exercise for our on-site medical facilities! Well, that's what they said anyway, but isn't this kind of weird...? I feel like I'd rather be taking care of others, not the other way around...

skins.name: Nereid's Discovery
skins.desc: "Let's go explore the ocean together! What special things will we be able to find today~?" Hehe, how's that, Commander?

skins.name: At Your Service
skins.desc: I hope your work's going well, Commander! I've been here playing with these kitties since finishing my duties. Here, I brewed some fresh tea to help you recharge~

skins.name: Jervis
skins.desc: J-class destroyer – Jervis.

skins.name: Fluttering in the Fair Breeze
skins.desc: Phew... That about does it. Next on the agenda is... Huh, Commander? What are you doing here?

skins.name: Janus
skins.desc: J-class destroyer – Janus.

skins.name: Fright-Night Scaredy-Cat
skins.desc: D-don't worry, Janus... There's no such thing as Halloween ghouls... Hyeep?! A c-cat?! *whimper*... Jervis, Commander, please come save me...!

skins.name: Fear of Changing... Clothes
skins.desc: It's okay, Janus. You're just getting dressed, so do it like usual, and everything will be fine... Hwuh? Commander? S-sorry! I'm the one who told you to keep your eyes closed, so why did I go and talk to you?!

skins.name: Hero
skins.desc: H-class destroyer – Hero.

skins.name: The Devil Wears Knee-Highs
skins.desc: Morning, Commander. Looks like our desks are right next to each other~ Whee~☆ Hmm? What's up? Is there something on my skirt? Teehee~♪

skins.name: Leander
skins.desc: Leander-class light cruiser – Leander, Hull Number 75!

skins.name: Leander (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Everything as you wish, Commander. Oh? Yes, I'm Leander!

skins.name: Achilles
skins.desc: Leander-class light cruiser – Achilles, Hull Number 70!

skins.name: Achilles (Retrofit)
skins.desc: The cute and charming Achilles is Super☆Retro☆Fitted! Even my heel won't give me any problems now! Well, not like it really ever did before, ahaha~☆

skins.name: Ajax
skins.desc: Leander-class light cruiser – Ajax, Hull Number 22!

skins.name: Party Queen
skins.desc: Ahaha, that slovenly expression on your face proves I made the right wardrobe choice♪ Now then, Commander, can I offer you some wine?

skins.name: Valentine's Reward?
skins.desc: I have some special chocolate right here, just~ for~ you. Hehe, if you want it so badly... then come and get it~

skins.name: Ajax (Retrofit)
skins.desc: I'll allow you to lick my feet since I'm in such a good mood today. What? I can't believe you'd turn down such a great opportunity!

skins.name: Dido
skins.desc: Dido-class light cruiser – Dido (HMS Dido.)

skins.name: Anxious Bisque Doll
skins.desc: It is so audacious for a lowly maid to dress herself in such finery and stand at her master's side... Still, I will go to my master and... M-M-Master...?!

skins.name: Southampton
skins.desc: Southampton-class light cruiser – Southampton.

skins.name: New Year's Little Knight
skins.desc: Hello there~! Royal Knight Southampton is reporting for duty in a Sakura-style outfit! Hehe, don't you have something to tell me about my new look, like how cute it is? Come on, don't be shy. Speak up~

skins.name: Afternoon Impromptu
skins.desc: Good day, Comm—Err, I guess it's "Master?" Ugh, I do prefer calling you Commander though... Anyway, I've been practicing the violin to help create better atmosphere around the shop. Did you come here because you were captivated by the sound of my music?

skins.name: A Dazzling Departure
skins.desc: The Royal Knight, Southampton, makes her grand entrance in glorious wedding garb~! Oh, Commander, you look a bit on edge. Here, c'mere for a second~ Ehehe. *rub rub* Well? Feeling a bit less stiff?

skins.name: Sheffield
skins.desc: Sheffield-class Light Cruiser - HMS Sheffield

skins.name: Cloak and Dagger
skins.desc: ... Did you find out about my undercover identity? You leave me no choice. Master, I cannot allow you to leave this room... Of course I'm jesting, it's merely a hobby.

skins.name: A Moment's Respite
skins.desc: The Sakura Empire's summer festivals... they're quite noisy. It will be difficult to keep things clean with so many people around... Despite that, I'm still having a good time. Is there a problem?

skins.name: Black Crow's Finery
skins.desc: The fact that you're asking your own maid to be your partner at the ball shows a concerning lack of gumption as a human being... However, if you go and make a fool of yourself, it will reflect poorly upon my standing as a maid. Therefore, I have no choice but to accompany you.

skins.name: Bulletborne
skins.desc: Allow me to warn you ahead of time, Master. I will not come to your rescue if you spring another trap, so please mind your step henceforth... Just kidding. It is a maid's duty to aid her master, after all.

skins.name: Manchester
skins.desc: Gloucester-class light cruiser – Manchester.

skins.name: Midnight Devil in White
skins.desc: Master, it's time for your injection! Hmm... Nowhere to be seen, eh... Then I guess I'll keep the sickbed warm until Master comes ba– Eep! M-M-Master?!

skins.name: Gloucester
skins.desc: Gloucester-class light cruiser – Gloucester (HMS Gloucester.)

skins.name: Brilliance in Purple
skins.desc: Gloucester, light cruiser of the Royal Maids, at your service for the Spring Festival... You say I look displeased? I beg your pardon, it's just... Such holidays are in fact quite busy for the Maids. We have much on our minds. It is none of your concern.

skins.name: Edinburgh
skins.desc: Edinburgh-Class light cruiser ー Edinburgh, Hull number 16!

skins.name: The Library Fairy
skins.desc: Why doesn't she have to go to school with me...she says she’s a maid for the Queen? Well, me too! You can be a maid and school girl at the same time...tsk tsk---

skins.name: Candy Maid
skins.desc: Ahem! I made this special candy just for Halloween! Here, Commander, take some! Wooaaooah! Wh-who put this pumpkin here? It, it was me?!

skins.name: Belfast
skins.desc: Edinburgh-Class light cruiser ー Belfast, Hull number C35!

skins.name: Iridescent Rosa
skins.desc: Hehe... Master, why are you so stunned from seeing me? I thought you perhaps wanted to see me in a qipao... was I mistaken?

skins.name: Serene Steel
skins.desc: This is special cold-weather equipment inspired by Eagle Union designs. It was made for practical purposes such as special operations in frigid climates, and as such, was not designed with appearances in mind. Please do forgive me, Master.

skins.name: The Noble Attendant
skins.desc: Good evening. The Royal Maids will be chaperoning this event. It is my hope to prevent any inappropriate behaviour that might interfere with the enjoyment of the attendees. Please pardon any inconveniences this may cause.

skins.name: Shopping with the Head Maid
skins.desc: Hehe~ Judging from your expression, Master, my outfit has not fallen short of your expectations. As time is precious, allow me to serve you to the utmost on this "date."

skins.name: Piping-Hot Perfection
skins.desc: Welcome, table for one? Of course, right this way. Oh? What is it? Ah... I'm filling in for the manager at the moment, so that makes you my customer rather than my master, no?

skins.name: Folded Fascination
skins.desc: It took me quite some time to prepare a suitable traditional Sakura Empire outfit. Terribly sorry. Master, won't you please allow this Belfast to serve you for another year?

skins.name: The Pledge of Claddagh
skins.desc: Are you destined for me? Greetings Belfast, from this moment onwards, I will always be with you.

skins.name: Arethusa
skins.desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Arethusa, Hull Number 26!

skins.name: Galatea
skins.desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Galatea, Hull Number 71!

skins.name: Aurora
skins.desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser - Aurora, pennant number 12

skins.name: The Tale of Spring
skins.desc: I've been preparing for this day for quite some time... Commander, would you like to hear the book I wrote for you?

skins.name: Dawn's Paean
skins.desc: I've always believed that music is unique in its power to touch one's heart, so I decided to learn the violin. Commander, please enjoy my performance.

skins.name: Heritage of Yu City
skins.desc: "Next, Aurora will perform something you've never seen before - traditional Sichuan mask-changing opera!" Hehe... Commander, I look like the real deal, right?

skins.name: Garb of Eternal Prosperity
skins.desc: Commander, please relax and take a seat. This is a special place for just the two of us... Just kidding, did I get your heart racing just now? Ehehe~

skins.name: Fiji
skins.desc: Fiji-class light cruiser – Fiji.

skins.name: Trendy and Vogue?
skins.desc: Did I keep you waiting, Commander? Ahaha... A girl's gotta take her time before stepping out onto the streets, remember? Come on, take my hand, and let's get going! Hehe~

skins.name: Jamaica
skins.desc: Fiji-class light cruiser – Jamaica.

skins.name: Dark Bolt
skins.desc: Hey Boss, you talkin' about my sweet bike? Heh, I made it myself by scrounging up parts from Akashi's place. Pretty cool, huh?

skins.name: Highway Star
skins.desc: Look, Boss, this is the new bike that Akashi sent me. She said she wanted me to be her brand ambassador... Doesn't that job sound badass?

skins.name: Little Bel
skins.desc: Edinburgh-class light cruiser – Belfast.

skins.name: Newcastle
skins.desc: Southampton-class light cruiser – Newcastle (HMS Newcastle.)

skins.name: Hibiscus Garments
skins.desc: This outfit makes me stand out a bit too much... But, as long as it makes you happy, I'm just as pleased.

skins.name: Newcastle (Retrofit)
skins.desc: I've got an all new outfit here. Does it please you...? Hehe, seeing you all giddy like that is going to rub off on me as well.

skins.name: Sirius
skins.desc: Dido-class light cruiser – Sirius.

skins.name: White Rose
skins.desc: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.

skins.name: Scorching-Hot Seirios
skins.desc: I've received ample advice from my colleagues in the Maid Team regarding swimwear etiquette. My honourable Master, are you pleased with my appearance?

skins.name: Azure Horizons
skins.desc: I have heard it is part of a maid's duties to dress to her honourable Master's liking over the holidays. Would this outfit happen to... satisfy the honourable Master's wishes?

skins.name: Curacoa
skins.desc: Ceres-class light cruiser - Curacoa (D41)

skins.name: Eastern Grace
skins.desc: As I am but a maid, it is a great honor to be able to wear such a gorgeous outfit… How do I look, Commander? "Not sure where to start feasting your eyes?" Oh my... Commander...

skins.name: Curacoa (Retrofit)
skins.desc: It is my honour to be of everyone's service. Light cruiser Curacoa takes it upon herself to continue serving you, Master.

skins.name: Curlew
skins.desc: Ceres-class light cruiser - Curlew (D42)

skins.name: Rhythm of the Dragon Empery
skins.desc: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.

skins.name: Curlew (Retrofit)
skins.desc: I am now more capable than ever of demonstrating the Royal Maids' style. Though I am not as talented as my sister, Curacoa, I sincerely hope you will find my service satisfactory. It is a great honour to work for you.

skins.name: Swiftsure
skins.desc: I am Swiftsure, a light cruiser of the Royal Navy... If it is not too much for one such as myself to ask, I would like to support your fleet in whatever way I can.

skins.name: Study Hall Cyclamen
skins.desc: Commander, why are you here...? Me? Yes, as you can see, I'm still studying... I figured that acquiring knowledge would be the best way to make up for my lack of experience on the actual battlefield.

skins.name: Beauty of White Jade
skins.desc: I agreed to try on this outfit, but... I know these fancy outfits don't suit me... H-huh, I look gorgeous?! ...Thank you very much. Even if you're just trying to make me feel better, I appreciate it...

skins.name: Midsummer Special Service
skins.desc: W-welcome! ...Ugh, I'm still way too nervous... Ah, um! H-how may I serve you today, Commander...?

skins.name: Black Prince
skins.desc: Err, you're... the Commander, yes? You don't know who I am? Ah, right, I've yet to introduce myself... I'm Black Prince of the Royal Navy... Will that suffice?

skins.name: White Princess
skins.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. Thank you very much for taking me on vacation. Standing in front of you like this... is a little embarrassing... Nevertheless, what do you think of... my swimsuit?

skins.name: Fair Maid Spring
skins.desc: A "qipao," is it? So this legendary dress from the Dragon Empery... Putting it on and enjoying some nostalgic music, makes me... Ahhh... Commander, might we relax like this a bit longer...?

skins.name: Pop the Cork
skins.desc: You can't have a party without champagne, right? Now, if I remember right, you're meant to give it a good shake before popping the cork... Oh no! Look out, Commander!

skins.name: Addled Attendant?
skins.desc: Oh... Welcome, Commander. Can I take your order...? Or maybe, you just wanted to kick back and relax? ...Either way is fine with me.

skins.name: Sheffield μ
skins.desc: I am Sheffield, from the Royal Maids. I will explain how this transpired to you, so please stop looking like the world has turned upside down.

skins.name: Cloak and Dagger
skins.desc: ... Did you find out about my undercover identity? You leave me no choice. Master, I cannot allow you to leave this room... Of course I'm jesting, it's merely a hobby.

skins.name: A Moment's Respite
skins.desc: The Sakura Empire's summer festivals... they're quite noisy. It will be difficult to keep things clean with so many people around... Despite that, I'm still having a good time. Is there a problem?

skins.name: Black Crow's Finery
skins.desc: The fact that you're asking your own maid to be your partner at the ball shows a concerning lack of gumption as a human being... However, if you go and make a fool of yourself, it will reflect poorly upon my standing as a maid. Therefore, I have no choice but to accompany you.

skins.name: Bulletborne
skins.desc: Allow me to warn you ahead of time, Master. I will not come to your rescue if you spring another trap, so please mind your step henceforth... Just kidding. It is a maid's duty to aid her master, after all.

skins.name: Glasgow
skins.desc: Southampton-class light cruiser - Glasgow (C-21)

skins.name: A Maid in Class
skins.desc: Y-ye said ye wanted ta see me wear something different, so... But this is not "cosplay" or somesuch! I do actually go to school...! D-do ye like it?

skins.name: Hermione
skins.desc: Dido-class light cruiser – Hermione (HMS Hermione.)

skins.name: Pure White Angel
skins.desc: My, what brings you here, Commander? Are you feeling unwell? That's no good... Why don't you come sit over here first? I'll start by taking your temperature...

skins.name: Pure White Holiday
skins.desc: Commander, I've brought the chair. If you don't want to get in the water, feel free to sit here. ...Hm, me? Of course, I will remain by your side.

skins.name: Graceful Afternoon Tea
skins.desc: Would you care for some afternoon tea, Commander? Heehee~ This is one of my little hobbies when I'm not performing my maid duties.

skins.name: Pristine Herbalist
skins.desc: How are you feeling, Commander? Hehe, I'm not wearing my usual nurse's gown right now, but I suppose this isn't much different~

skins.name: Dido µ
skins.desc: I am the light cruiser, Dido, currently taking part in idol activities as part of the experimental Muse System. I learned more or less what idols are supposed to do from the others, so p-please... keep a close eye on me!

skins.name: Anxious Bisque Doll
skins.desc: It is so audacious for a lowly maid to dress herself in such finery and stand at her master's side... Still, I will go to my master and... M-M-Master...?!

skins.name: Penelope
skins.desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Penelope.

skins.name: Ruby-Red Boudoir
skins.desc: Aurora chose this outfit for me because... the Spring Festival represents a time of celebration in the Dragon Empery, and red is the color that best symbolizes that. What do you think? Does this outfit... make you feel more festive?

skins.name: Salty Maid
skins.desc: Welcome, welcome. I've been working here as a maid, just as you told me to. Umm... Call for me only when you're ready to order.

skins.name: Charybdis
skins.desc: Dido-class light cruiser – Charybdis.

skins.name: Red Chamber of Healing
skins.desc: *Pats thighs* Master, you poor thing~ Look how hard you've been working~ Hehe, hurry and come here so that I can pamper you~

skins.name: Brilliant Belle
skins.desc: Tis a pleasure to see you, Master. I am delighted to be your partner for today. ...Oh, I was just trying to sound prim and proper! You don't need to look at me with such pity in your eyes!

skins.name: Prim Sea Breeze
skins.desc: As you can see, today's theme... is a seaside pampering, or something like that~ Heehee. I know you're no stranger to the sea, Commander, but today, we're here to play, not work. Just take it easy, and unwind~♪

skins.name: Bellona
skins.desc: Bellona-class light cruiser – Bellona.

skins.name: Armed to Clean
skins.desc: My liege... No, excuse me, I should be calling you Master, right? Bellona of the Royal Maids, reporting in. My, you seem quite lost for words... I'll explain the situation to you later, so don't worry about it.

skins.name: Enterprise
skins.desc: Emerald-class light cruiser –Enterprise.

skins.name: Scylla
skins.desc: Dido-class light cruiser – Scylla.

skins.name: Femme Fatale Fresher
skins.desc: Did you come all this way just because I asked you to, Master? Or... would you prefer I call you "Senpai" here? If we're at school, then there's no reason for me to act maidly, now is there? Heeheehee♪

skins.name: London
skins.desc: London-class heavy cruiser – London, Hull Number 69!

skins.name: Platinum Ceremony
skins.desc: Why are you so astounded, Your Excellency? You expressly requested an unforgettable and elaborate ceremony. Heehee, you'll make it weird if you keep staring so much, so won't you please take my hand now?

skins.name: London (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Um... Your Excellency, could you please stop staring at me like you don't recognise me? I didn't think that I'd get a new look for my retrofit, either... But, don't you think it's rather cute?

skins.name: Shropshire
skins.desc: London-class heavy cruiser – Shropshire, Hull Number 73!

skins.name: Shropshire (Retrofit)
skins.desc: As you know, I'm the youngest of London class, Shropshire~ I'm excited to work with you! Heheh, I look pretty capable now, don't I? Maybe I'll cause a little less trouble for you now, Commander!

skins.name: Kent
skins.desc: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Kent, Hull Number 54!

skins.name: Suffolk
skins.desc: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Suffolk, Hull Number 55!

skins.name: Suffolk (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Whew... At long last, after all that hard work, I get to wear this uniform as well. Even though all I did was... Huh? Lead by example? Be a role model? I don't get it...

skins.name: Norfolk
skins.desc: Norfolk-class heavy cruiser - Norfolk, Hull Number 78!

skins.name: Dorsetshire
skins.desc:
Norfolk-class heavy cruiser, Dorsetshire, Hull Number 40
<color=#fad545>Unlock build after receiving

skins.name: York
skins.desc: York-class heavy cruiser - York, Hull Number 90!

skins.name: Truth Seeker
skins.desc: The school has recently been consumed by a series of Mysteries... there must be some Mastermind lurking behind the scenes. Yes, another Tribulation awaits me! I shall part the veil and reveal all Truths!

skins.name: Summoner from the Azure Depths
skins.desc: O Unfathomable King of the slumbering depths, hear the call of my Force and step into this world through the Azur Gate! ...Huh, Commander? Why did you show up?

skins.name: Oath of Purity
skins.desc: Whoa... Is this my Uniform for the ceremony known as the Oath of Purity? Hohoho... This must be fate. Join me, Commander, and we shall make the world right once more!

skins.name: York (Retrofit)
skins.desc: This is no mere Upgrade, this is an Awakening! I will alter the course of fate itself!

skins.name: Exeter
skins.desc: York-class heavy cruiser - Exeter, Hull Number 68!

skins.name: A Glorious Toast
skins.desc: Cheers, Commander. I'm glad that the party is a success. Well, I should take care as well to not sully the honour of the royal family with my actions.

skins.name: Exeter (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Commander, what do you think? I look more mature than I did before... right?

skins.name: Sussex
skins.desc: London-class heavy cruiser, Sussex. Hull Number 96.

skins.name: Sunlit Tulips
skins.desc: What are you spacing out for? Have you not gotten tired of staring at all the swimsuits yet? Good grief... Are you able to help set up the parasol or the beach chairs at least?

skins.name: Wine and Red Roses
skins.desc: What are you staring at me for? I'm just the same as any of the others... Y-you have a few more hands to shake? Of course...

skins.name: Little Cheshire
skins.desc: Heavy cruiser – Cheshire.

skins.name: Renown
skins.desc: Renown-class battlecruiser - Renown

skins.name: Repulse
skins.desc: Renown-class battlecruiser - Repulse

skins.name: Hood
skins.desc: Admiral-class battlecruiser - Hood, Hull Number 51!

skins.name: Lady of the Shining Sun
skins.desc: What a feast for sore eyes. I feel great~! Vacations really should be at the beach! Let's show Sara your beach ball, Cygnet!

skins.name: Porcelain Grace
skins.desc: Thank you for inviting me on this wonderful trip. Now that I have donned this beautiful outfit, shall we partake of a Sakura Empire tea party– leisurely and elegantly?

skins.name: Dawnlight's Dame
skins.desc: Beauty is not always over the rainbow. Sometimes it is right in your backyard. Commander, how would you like to spend this quiet, lovely day right here with me?

skins.name: Rosey Love Poem
skins.desc: If the smooth path only allows one person to travel at a time, then I’ll gladly walk the path not taken with you hand-in-hand.

skins.name: Little Renown
skins.desc: Renown-Class Battlecruiser - HMS Renown

skins.name: Queen Elizabeth
skins.desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Queen Elizabeth, Hull Number 00!

skins.name: The Queen's Ball
skins.desc: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!

skins.name: One Night of the Queen
skins.desc: Now this is a stage worthy of our majesty! You are not to leave our sight, servant! Let your passions burn for me!

skins.name: Queen of the Campus
skins.desc: Hehe, behold the new outfit that I had Akashi make for me! Impressive, no? Prostrate yourself before the elegant charm of my school uniform, servant~♪

skins.name: Crown Jewel of the Royal Navy
skins.desc: Did I hear that you're supposed to give out red envelopes during the Dragon Empery's New Year? This is a fine chance to display the magnanimity of the Queen of the Royal Navy! ...Don't just run off with your gift! Spread the word of my glory, my servant!

skins.name: Yes, Your Maidness!
skins.desc: Warspite, what in the world is all this... The Maid Team has to sift through all this paperwork?! I'm tired already... I wish I never mentioned wanting to experience what it's like to be a maid... And you, stop staring and help me already, servant!

skins.name: 伊丽莎白占坑
skins.desc: 占坑

skins.name: Warspite
skins.desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Warspite, Hull Number 03!

skins.name: Christmas Warrior
skins.desc: This year, I am in charge of delivering presents to the children of the Royal Navy. Let's get going once I finish decorating this Christmas tree!

skins.name: Under Pleasure
skins.desc: We have the finest equipment. Now to turn in a performance worthy of Her Majesty's beauty... Behold, the Royal Stage!

skins.name: Warspite (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Warspite, retrofitting complete. Mm, I rather like this feeling of being rejuvenated... Now, Commander, let us make our way towards new battlegrounds!

skins.name: Nelson
skins.desc: Nelson-class battleship – Nelson, Hull Number 28!

skins.name: Luna Witch
skins.desc: This is such a weird costume… oh well, it’s Halloween after all. It cannot be so bad, this is a fun activity after all. First things first, I didn’t say that I would join from the very beginning!

skins.name: Azure & Gold Summer Night
skins.desc: Hey, are you even enjoying yourself? At least pretend to have fun when I went out of my way to invite you, or else I'm going to lose sleep over this! ...Look behind me? What are you– Oh...!

skins.name: Rodney
skins.desc: Nelson-class battleship – Rodney, Hull Number 29!

skins.name: Future Seaside Admiral
skins.desc: Although it's a gift from the Commander, it's still embarrassing to wear this....Commander, do you think you could teach me how to swim?

skins.name: Immaculate Beauty
skins.desc: Miss Akashi, shall I look at the camera next? Understood. Oh, Commander, I did not expect you to grace us with your presence here as well! Yes, the photoshoot is proceeding smoothly. By the way, is there a favorite pose you'd like to see?

skins.name: Palace of Blessings
skins.desc: I never imagined that this dreamlike situation would come to pass... Commander, have you also been looking forward to sharing this moment with me? Hehe~

skins.name: King George V
skins.desc: King George V-class battleship – King George V.

skins.name: Rose's Regalia
skins.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander... I don't get to wear a dress very often, so it took me a bit longer. Let's get going, then. Remember, you'll be the lead tonight. Haha~

skins.name: Prince of Wales
skins.desc: King George V-class battleship – Prince of Wales, Hull Number 53!

skins.name: Sun Shining Upon Windsor
skins.desc: I'm not a big fan of beach volleyball, but Hood begged me... I swear, that girl! She just can't get enough of the sun! You've got to cheer for me!

skins.name: Sakura Elegance
skins.desc: I've been wearing Royal attire my whole life, so a change in pace doesn't seem bad. Oh, Commander, good timing. Can you explain to me how to celebrate the New Year here?

skins.name: The Laureate's Victory Lap
skins.desc: Oh, Commander. Worry not. Since I've been given this job, I will see through it until the end. Besides, it's been a while since I've gotten this fired up. Haha!

skins.name: Duke of York
skins.desc: King George V-class battleship - HMS Duke of York.

skins.name: Eternal Night's Carola
skins.desc: Ahh, this luscious scent... comes from thee. What dost thee feel when gazing upon my new dress? Hehe... your lips may lie but your eyes do not...

skins.name: Prestige of the Glorious Formula
skins.desc: My beautiful Adonis, why dost thou refuseth to take refuge in the trove of everlasting love... Perhaps my outfit can finally pierce thy heart? Hehe~

skins.name: Howe
skins.desc: King George V-class battleship – Howe (HMS Howe.)

skins.name: Noble Rouge
skins.desc: Sorry to keep you waiting, but now I'm ready to– Commander? What's the matter? It'll get dark soon if you keep standing around like that.

skins.name: Pastry Princess
skins.desc: "Please, Master, save meee." ...Ugh, I can't get into the role. What sort of tone should I be aiming for, love?

skins.name: Evening Marvels
skins.desc: Thanks for your patience, love. I've looked forward to this evening's party for a long, long time. Hopefully George, York, and company won't laugh at me after how much effort I've put into this ensemble... What do you think of it, Commander?

skins.name: Valiant
skins.desc: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship – Valiant (HMS Valiant.)

skins.name: Mischievous Little Nurse
skins.desc: Hehe~ As this medical facility training is crucially important, a charismatic leader such as myself would be best suited to instruct everyone on– Wait a moment, what's with this outfit?! You there, explain the meaning of this at once!

skins.name: Queen Valiant I
skins.desc: Why the astonished look on your face? You heard me correctly! On this day, I am not merely Valiant, I am the regal and royal Queen Valiant!

skins.name: Revenge
skins.desc: R-class battleship – Revenge.

skins.name: The Maid-Knight Charges Forth!
skins.desc: Hrmm... *sigh*... Looks like I bungled this one too... I sure hope the Commander doesn't see me like th– Hwuh?! C-Commander? P-please give me a moment! I'll straighten this out right away... Waaah!!

skins.name: Vanguard
skins.desc: Battleship – Vanguard.

skins.name: Half-Hearted Masquerade
skins.desc: "Please let me know if you need anything, Master"... I'm starting to think you're making me wear this as a sick joke. The reason being, I am obviously NOT fit to be a Royal Maid... Even if I do adore their uniforms...

skins.name: Royal Oak
skins.desc: R-class battleship – Royal Oak.

skins.name: Bashful Oak
skins.desc: Commander? Oh, what a coincidence... Were you slacking– err, I mean, taking a break, too? I can make some room for you if you'd like?

skins.name: Hermes
skins.desc: Hermes-class aircraft carrier – Hermes, Hull Number 95!

skins.name: Hermes (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Our glory coalesces into the bonds that forge a bright new future! Let's rev it up! Hermes, retrofit complete!

skins.name: Argus
skins.desc: Light aircraft carrier – Argus.

skins.name: A Hundred Sleepless Eyes
skins.desc: Yaaawn... Umm, did I doze off again? Oh no... Organising school events gets so hectic I always end up working right up until curfew... Just give me one more minute, please...

skins.name: Unicorn
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier – Unicorn, Hull Number I72!

skins.name: Little Star Songstress
skins.desc: Unicorn... is now a songstress... *giggles* Unicorn's song has reached Onii-chan's heart.

skins.name: The Gift of Spring
skins.desc: This... present... is for you... I hope you like it... What? Me wearing this outfit is the best gift I can give you? Co... Commander!...

skins.name: Long-Awaited Date
skins.desc: Ah, big brother, you're here... Ehehe, I only just got here as well. Um... shall we go then? I kind of... want to go to the amusement park...

skins.name: Prayer of Plum and Snow
skins.desc: So this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire... Changing into it is difficult but... if you like it, then Unicorn is happy!

skins.name: Angelic Night
skins.desc: So I'm... an "idol" now... I'm not sure how well I'll do... But I'll give it my all...!

skins.name: Icy-Sweet Storytime
skins.desc: Oh, big brother... Unicorn is reading right now. Mm, yeah, while eating ice cream... Big brother, want to have a bite?

skins.name: A Dream of Pure Vows
skins.desc: This is... an important outfit for an important ceremony... yes! Unicorn and Yuni are both ready for this! Big brother... how do I look?

skins.name: Unicorn (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Unicorn has finished her retrofit... Now she can do more for you and her friends!

skins.name: Centaur
skins.desc: Centaur-class light aircraft carrier – Centaur.

skins.name: Beachside Undine
skins.desc: Even though I see the ocean every day, changing into this swimsuit gives me a totally new outlook on it. How about you, Commander? Don't you feel at ease?

skins.name: Sprightly Spring Wind
skins.desc: I never imagined you would give me such a splendid dress, Commander... I think it's called a "qipao..." is it? I'll try it, revealing though it is. Wh- what do you think...? Do I look... nice?

skins.name: Chaser
skins.desc: Attacker-class escort carrier - Chaser (D32)

skins.name: The Way of the Dragon Empery
skins.desc: Does this dress from the Dragon Empery not suit me well? Though I was born in the Eagle Union and raised by the Royal Navy, my time in the Dragon Empery also left a deep impression upon me. Why don't we have a chat about their profound culture and tea? Hehe~

skins.name: Gamer Style
skins.desc: Heck yeah! Another achievement down! ...Huh? Good day, Commander. Is there something wrong with my appearance? Hehe, I'm from the Eagle Union after all, of course I'd know a thing or two about entertainment~♪

skins.name: Perseus
skins.desc: Colossus-class light aircraft carrier – Perseus (HMS Perseus.)

skins.name: Unfamiliar Duties
skins.desc: I'm Perseus, I will be your nurse today. Use this button to call for me if you need anything... Yes? Did you need something?

skins.name: Albion
skins.desc: Centaur-class light aircraft carrier – Albion.

skins.name: Silvermoon Faerie Princess
skins.desc: Ah, umm... If you keep staring at me like that... Oh, um, Commander, this is supposed to be a Royalty of the Night costume, right? In that case... Would you mind kneeling for me first?

skins.name: Theseus
skins.desc: Colossus-class light carrier – Theseus.

skins.name: New Year's White Plumage
skins.desc: Steaming hot manjuu buns, ready to be served! Let us have a big feast then gather rosebuds, Commander. Oh, a "holiday gathering" doesn't involve literal gathering?

skins.name: Eagle
skins.desc: Eagle-class light aircraft carrier – Eagle (HMS Eagle.)

skins.name: Eagle's Clinic
skins.desc: This may be an exercise, but even so I will give it my all. Right now, I am not just a Royal Navy warrior, but a medical resident as well. If you ever feel ill, come see me, Commander.

skins.name: Ark Royal
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier – Ark Royal, Hull Number 91!

skins.name: Coast Watcher
skins.desc: Nothing says summer like the sun, the beach, and destroyers... Ahem! Th-that's right! Even though we're relaxing, we still have to keep an eye out for enemy destroyers! Commander, I may be in a swimsuit, but I'm ready to sortie at any time!

skins.name: Guardian of the Ball
skins.desc: One tends to let her guard down at a party like this, but worry not! Put the ball in my hands and let Ark Royal keep you safe!

skins.name: New Year's Protectress
skins.desc: Commander, Happy New Year. Oh no, I'm not going hunting. I'm patrolling the port during the New Year's celebrations. Naturally, I volunteered for the job.

skins.name: Café Lookout
skins.desc: This is the place, Commander. What are you going to order? Me, I think I'll have the same as you... Yeah, so what? I just felt like grabbing a coffee with you for once.

skins.name: Pure-White Protector
skins.desc: I never thought a day would come when even I don such attire... Ahem. Your Excellency, I shall protect your happiness, as well as that of my destroyer sisters!

skins.name: Ark Royal (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Ark Royal retrofitting complete! Now I can protect you, my friends, and of course, the little destroyers, to the very end!

skins.name: Illustrious
skins.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87!

skins.name: Never-Ending Tea Party
skins.desc: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?

skins.name: Illustrious Ball
skins.desc: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, I would be honored to go... as long as you don't decline, Commander~

skins.name: Resplendent Hibiscus
skins.desc: This is my first time wearing such exotic fashion, hehe~. Commander, if you like how I look, how about showing me off a little~?

skins.name: Maiden Lily's Radiance
skins.desc: It is my honour to get to wear another faction's garments. However... this traditional Dragon Empery dress feels rather tight around the chest area...

skins.name: Morning Star of Love and Hope
skins.desc: The end of sorrow, the beginning of happiness, and the desire for eternity.

skins.name: Victorious
skins.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Victorious.

skins.name: The Goddess' Day Off
skins.desc: Hum~ dee dum♪~ I'm all dressed up, and my hair is perfect! Commander, I'm ready to go! Don't keep me waiting on a holiday!

skins.name: Guidance of the Spring Goddess
skins.desc: Are you preparing to hold an event for the port? Hehe, sounds like you could use my help. Don't worry, with someone as beautiful as me around, anything you do will surely be blessed with success!

skins.name: Formidable
skins.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Formidable.

skins.name: The Lady of the Beach
skins.desc: Good day, Commander. I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. Pleased to make your acquaintance.

skins.name: Timeless Classics
skins.desc: Yes, this will do wonderfully! Thank you, ladies. Phew... Getting dressed is so dreadfully time-consuming... Ahem! How silly of me. I must not whine in the presence of others.

skins.name: Glorious
skins.desc: Courageous-class aircraft carrier – Glorious, Hull Number 77.

skins.name: Glorious School Life
skins.desc: Being able to occasionally have a peaceful school life... is something I could get used to. Commander, look at the markings on this butterfly - aren't they lovely?

skins.name: Pungent Plum
skins.desc: I heard that the Sakura Empire's traditional attire was really hard to put on... but the Dragon's Empery's outfits are even more... Huh?! Commander, p-please look away!

skins.name: Implacable
skins.desc: Implacable-class aircraft carrier – Implacable.

skins.name: Shepherd of the "Lost"
skins.desc: Oh my... It seems I've shown you a rather unseemly side of me. Would you help me clean up here, Commander? You know... before any of the other girls find out. Heehee~♥

skins.name: Little Illustrious
skins.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87.

skins.name: Illustrious μ
skins.desc: I am the newest addition to the Muse System, Illustrious. Through my songs, I shall spread the light of love and peace— Don't you think that's a wonderful thing?

skins.name: Never-Ending Tea Party
skins.desc: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?

skins.name: Illustrious Ball
skins.desc: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, I would be honored to go... as long as you don't decline, Commander~

skins.name: Resplendent Hibiscus
skins.desc: This is my first time wearing such exotic fashion, hehe~. Commander, if you like how I look, how about showing me off a little~?

skins.name: Maiden Lily's Radiance
skins.desc: It is my honour to get to wear another faction's garments. However... this traditional Dragon Empery dress feels rather tight around the chest area...

skins.name: Indomitable
skins.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Indomitable.

skins.name: Ms. Motivationless Maid
skins.desc: *Sigh*... I thought changing into maid attire would break up the monotony, but just getting into these clothes has tired me out... Oh, Commander? You came at a good time. Shall we slack off together?

skins.name: Erebus
skins.desc: Erebus-class monitor – Erebus, Hull Number I02!

skins.name: Illusory Happiness
skins.desc: Those who embrace the shadows will find only an illusory happiness... But for me, that much is sufficient.

skins.name: Wardrobe Witchery
skins.desc: "I am the witch of Hallow's Eve, here to guide your soul into the ever darkness"... that's what the concept of the Halloween witch is about, right?

skins.name: Terror
skins.desc: Erebus-class monitor – Terror, Hull Number I03!

skins.name: Halloween Terror
skins.desc: I have to dress up as a ghost for Halloween, but I'm not very good at making complicated costumes... Is something like this okay?

skins.name: Abercrombie
skins.desc: Roberts-class monitor - Abercrombie. Hull Number F109.

skins.name: Pumpkin Blast!
skins.desc: Kabooom! You thought it was a pumpkin, but it was me, Abercrombie, with my Mark I! Commander, did I scare you senseless? Muahaha!

skins.name: Mischief on the Rocks
skins.desc: Now for a ghost pepper while nobody's looking... Tee hee! Perfect! I wonder who'll be the lucky one to sip– C-Commander?! You didn't see anything suspicious... Right? Tee hee~

skins.name: Neptune
skins.desc: Light cruiser – Neptune.

skins.name: Princess of the Reindeers
skins.desc: Hehe~ I usually let the other girls have all the glory, but even I must sometimes give you something to remember me by. Merry Christmas, Commander~

skins.name: Nereid's Invitation
skins.desc: Welcome to our celebration, Commander. At this breathtaking venue, I, Neptune, shall be the one to show you around, rather than the Royal Maids. Heehee~♪

skins.name: Monarch
skins.desc: Battleship – Monarch.

skins.name: White Warrick
skins.desc: Hmph. One's outfit is merely superficial. True nobility must come from within. Don't you agree, Commander?

skins.name: Black Gerard
skins.desc: So, an Eastern outfit this time... Hmph. My nobility is evident regardless of what I wear. However, since you prepared this outfit especially for me, it would be unbecoming of me to not express my gratitude. Thank you.

skins.name: Cheshire
skins.desc: Heavy cruiser – Cheshire.

skins.name: Summery Date!
skins.desc: Cheer up, Owner! Jeez, why are you so bummed out when we're at the beach... Because it's just a normal playdate instead of a romantic date? What's the difference anyway? C'mon, let's go head down to where the others are~!

skins.name: Cait Sith Crooner
skins.desc: I'll sing a song for you, Owner~ Ahem... Wait, I'm not sure I know any Dragon Empery songs, actually...

skins.name: The Cat and the White Steed
skins.desc: "Owner~ I've come to take you to the ball~" ...That's exactly what you were going to do? Eh, doesn't matter who does it~ All that matters is we'll be there together~♪

skins.name: Drake
skins.desc: Heavy cruiser – Drake.

skins.name: The Golden Hind's Respite
skins.desc: Phew... Swimming like this doesn't feel all that refreshing... Hey, how about you stop staring and come join me?

skins.name: Plymouth
skins.desc: Light Cruiser—Plymouth

skins.name: Heart-Throbbing Refreshment
skins.desc: Rejoice, Commander. I have no doubt that this refreshing sensation will bring you the utmost satisfaction. Come, let us enjoy this experience together.

skins.name: Fubuki
skins.desc: Special type I Fubuki Destroyer Class— Fubuki

skins.name: 5 Minutes Till I'm Late
skins.desc: Oh no! I-I'm gonna be late for school! Y-you need to speed up too, doggy! *Pant*... *pant*... Why'd none of my sisters wake me up before they left?!

skins.name: Mascot Bucky
skins.desc: "C-come on in! We've got special offers for you!" ... W-wait, is this really what a "sexy mascot" would wear? It feels pretty different from what I was expecting... And boy, is it stuffy in this thing...

skins.name: Music Pixy
skins.desc: Check it out, Commander! What do you think? ... No, not my dress! I'm talking about the tuba! Want me to play a tune for you~?

skins.name: Fubuki Halation!
skins.desc: The whole world's going to feel the tremors from my debut! I'm Fubuki, the Special-type idol!

skins.name: Stormy Waitress-in-Training!
skins.desc: Welcome, welcome! Oh, Commander! I've actually started working here part-time, but I'm still learning— Wooah?! Phew... Th-that was a close one...

skins.name: Shirayuki
skins.desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number two – Shirayuki.

skins.name: Bunny Breeder
skins.desc: Whoa now! There's enough food for everyone, so don't fight over it! ...Commander? Don't just stand there, give me a hand, please!

skins.name: Miyuki
skins.desc: Special Type I Fubuki-class destroyer number four – Miyuki.

skins.name: Shopping Rendezvous
skins.desc: Commander, I think the goods over here are a bit cheaper... Umm, I'm doing fine on my budget still, so we can pick out some more things to buy. A-also, I'll get to spend more time shopping with you... Ah, d-disregard that please... *blushes*

skins.name: Ayanami
skins.desc: First ship of special Type II Ayanami class destroyers, Ayanami.

skins.name: Witch in Ambush
skins.desc: I heard that... I need to wear a costume like this to participate in Halloween festivities. Commander... do I look cute?

skins.name: Rock 'n' Demon
skins.desc: Commander, want to listen to music together? Do you like... this non-combat-oriented Ayanami?

skins.name: Lunar Demon
skins.desc: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?

skins.name: Grade A Sailor Uniform
skins.desc: "Welcome, Commander..." I should greet customers like this... yes?

skins.name: Covert Ops Cloak
skins.desc: Ayanami here. Successfully infiltrated Commander's office. Oh... Commander saw me. Operation failed...

skins.name: Low-Key Idol @Confused
skins.desc: I guess I'm making my idol debut? Um, Javelin and the others are making their debuts, so, I also had to... Commander, what are idols supposed to do normally?

skins.name: Demon's Finest Dress
skins.desc: This dress is... Ayanami’s. I'm not used to this dress yet... Commander, do you think it fits me?

skins.name: Ayanami (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be spoiled a bit...

skins.name: Pulse of the New Year
skins.desc: Commander, Happy New Year's. In this coming year, please continue to look after me...

skins.name: Nightfall Raiment
skins.desc: Commander, thank you for coming to the party. Ayanami... has been waiting for you. ...I look a bit scary? I'm not sure I get it... I guess.

skins.name: Off-Duty Battle Station Gear
skins.desc: No, Ryuujou! Samurai builds should stay back during the boss! ...Oh, welcome, Commander. I'm busy with this game right now, so just make yourself at home or something.

skins.name: Dynasty Shipgirl
skins.desc: Rigging, activate!

skins.name: Cola Fills You With Determination
skins.desc: Welcome. Ayanami will be taking your order, yes. Will this be dine-in, or to-go? I would personally recommend the cola.

skins.name: Dynamic Kick!
skins.desc: Ultimate Ability: Dynamic Kick! ...Oh, I used my skill on the wrong target. Sorry, can we try that again?

skins.name: Akatsuki
skins.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number one - Akatsuki.

skins.name: Akatsuki Goes North
skins.desc: Is this the place called the Northern Parliament?! It is colder than I thought... Th-thank goodness I brought gear for extreme environments! Hibiki, please wait a bit longer! Your sister is coming to see you!

skins.name: Motoninja Akatsuki
skins.desc: What do you think, Commander? I have a brand new outfit and a brand new companion! I am no longer a plain old ninja... I am now a motoninja!

skins.name: Santa's Lost Helper!
skins.desc: Look out! Move, Commander! ...Phew. To explain, I am helping Santa give out Christmas presents! Now excuse me, I cannot tarry here or I'll be late... Wait, have I come to the wrong place? WHAT?!

skins.name: Cirque de Ninjutsu!
skins.desc: Welcome, Commander, to DesDiv 6's tent of entertainment! For our first act, I shall perform for you my most stunning ninjutsu! ..."Circus"? I've never heard of this word before!

skins.name: Hibiki
skins.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number two – Hibiki.

skins.name: New Year's Little Imp
skins.desc: New Year's finally comes to port! I, Hibiki of the 6th DesDiv, will be marking my new arrival in my New Year's attire! Commander, don't you dare change the channel - you've gotta watch my every move~!

skins.name: Ikazuchi
skins.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number three - Ikazuchi.

skins.name: Sakura Tea
skins.desc: Ikazuchi, Ikazuchi has been transformed into tea! What should we do! Inazuma and Ikazuchi will get slurped up by the Commander!

skins.name: Thunderous Festival
skins.desc: Inazuma and I have been to a lot of festivals together, but this would be the first time that I've gone with you, Commander. Isn't this totally like a date?

skins.name: Dawn's Thunder
skins.desc: I'm the fairy of thunder that shatters the night to herald the dawn! I see, I see! That is a good backstory! Commander, want to head to the party together?

skins.name: Inazuma
skins.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number four - Inazuma.

skins.name: Vanilla Pudding
skins.desc: It doesn’t matter if Inazuma becomes Mr. Commander's dessert… but if Inazuma cannot be found, Mr. Commander will feel so devastated, perhaps he won’t be able to command the fleet… so… please! Please convey Inazuma's heartfelt wish to Mr. Commander——

skins.name: Flash of Fireworks
skins.desc: I usually go to festivals with Ikazuchi, but this would be my first time going with you. Hmm? Where should we visit first?

skins.name: Dusk's Lightning
skins.desc: I'm the fairy of lightning that illuminates the stars in the night sky... So that's what we're going with, huh. Commander, will you accompany me to the party?

skins.name: Shiratsuyu
skins.desc: Shiratsuyu-class destroyer number one - Shiratsuyu.

skins.name: Is The Order A Torpedo?
skins.desc: H-here they come... Your order, and your cutesy dutesy maid... Whoaahh! I'm sorry! Look out!

skins.name: Yuudachi
skins.desc: Shiratsuyu-class destroyer number four - Yuudachi.

skins.name: Shogun of Snowballs
skins.desc: Come out of your office, Commander! You'll become lazy if you huddle up next to the heater all day! Let's go out and play in the snow!

skins.name: Carnivore Carnival!
skins.desc: Commander, look at me, look at me! What do you think of my new outfit? If you like it, wanna give it a feel?

skins.name: Woofy Floofy Christmas Night
skins.desc: Christmas! The day Santa Claus drops by and leaves presents, right? Hell yeah, I'm pumped! Aren't you pumped too, Commander?

skins.name: The Bride of Solomon
skins.desc: Commander, look! Look at this new dress. Red and white, I really really like it! But what's the occasion?

skins.name: Yuudachi (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Woof...? Am I imagining it, or did you get shorter, Commander? Unless... it's me who's gotten bigger? Seriously?! Nobody told me retrofitting makes you taller!

skins.name: Shigure
skins.desc: Shiratsuyu-class destroyer number two - Shigure.

skins.name: Attack, I-490!
skins.desc: Stupid Commander, I'm not a damn submarine! Do you wanna get hit in the face with an oxygen torpedo?

skins.name: The Ballroom's Lucky Star
skins.desc: Oh my. Commander, you must be pretty lucky to bump into me here, hehe~ Since you're here, you can have the privilege of being my escort tonight. Now, be grateful~♪

skins.name: Lucky Chocolate
skins.desc: All right, that should be good... Hey, stupid Commander standing around aimlessly. Yeah, you. Stick your hand out. You're gonna be the first person to get MY chocolate, so I'd better see some tears of gratitude.

skins.name: Shigure (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Heheh~ Retrofitting the mighty Shigure proves that you are quite perceptive! Aren't you glad that you get to rely on me more, you lucky idiot of a commander~♪

skins.name: Yukikaze
skins.desc: Kagerou-class Destroyer no. 8 - Yukikaze

skins.name: Sovereign of the Swing
skins.desc: Wa ha ha! My "universal-as-long-as-there-is-a-ceiling" swing set is finally complete! Commander, are you jealous? Want to give it a try? Too~ bad~! This seat is reserved only for the noble and elegant Yukikaze!

skins.name: Winter's Snowy Wind
skins.desc: Wa ha ha~! Did your heart skip a beat from seeing the charming Yukikaze? Hmph... Well, looks like the Dragon Empery girls are setting off firecrackers... let's go join them! Here, make sure to hold on to my hand!

skins.name: The Warmth of Spring
skins.desc: This outfit is sooo cute~ ehehe... Ack!! *cough* *cough*! Ahem! From now on, you are the faithful companion of Yukikaze the Great! As such, you will not be permitted to leave my side, understood?

skins.name: Kagerou
skins.desc: Kagerou-class destroyer number one - Kagerou.

skins.name: Pumpkins and Festivities!
skins.desc: Commander, trick or treat! I expect you to give some candy to my sisters as well! These will-o'-wisps? Hahaha~ I tried imitating that gloomy sister of mine!

skins.name: Kagerou (Retrofit)
skins.desc: The newly-retrofitted Kagerou has arrived~ I won't let that sister of mine pass me up anymore! Commander, lead us forward towards distant shores!

skins.name: Shiranui
skins.desc: Kagerou-class destroyer number two - Shiranui.

skins.name: Mooncake Merchant
skins.desc: I see a chance... to capitalize on the Dragon Empery's famous mooncakes... Commander, would you like to have a taste of the Moon Palace's delicacies? If you buy them in bulk, I'll give you a special discount.

skins.name: Shiranui (Retrofit)
skins.desc: If you have this much money remaining... then you may visit me and spend it with confidence... A discount, you say...? Of course... Someday, I shall give you one...

skins.name: Nowaki
skins.desc: Kagerou-class destroyer number fifteen - Nowaki.

skins.name: Hatsuharu
skins.desc: Hatsuharu-class destroyer number one – Hatsuharu.

skins.name: Snow Day Hatsuharu
skins.desc: Everyone's playing together...? I-I think I'll pass... Y-you want me to join them? Ugh, well, if you say so, then I-I-I'll try to socialize with them...!

skins.name: Hatsuharu in the Limelight
skins.desc: C-Commander, I will be your partner for the party tonight. Let's see, umm... I believe this is proper Royal Navy etiquette... D-did I do it correctly?

skins.name: Hatsuharu (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Hatsuharu, retrofit complete... H-hopefully I'm a little bit stronger now...

skins.name: Wakaba
skins.desc: Hatsuharu-class destroyer number three – Wakaba.

skins.name: Holiday Special Wakaba!
skins.desc: Yaho~ Good morning, Commander! For a limited time only, Wakaba Claus will be delivering Christmas presents! Huh? My bag? Aaahhh! C-Commander, help me pick everything up!

skins.name: A Healthy Dose of Sunshine!
skins.desc: Hmmgh! Oh yeah... Ah, there you are, Commander! Care to join me? Come bask in the afternoon sunshine, it feels great!

skins.name: Hatsushimo
skins.desc: Hatsuharu-class Destroyer, number 4 - Hatsushimo

skins.name: Perennial Joy
skins.desc: Cheers, Commander~ C'mere, you've got to enjoy the party too! If you're thinking of doing something tactless like running off to go back to work, people are going to get upset with you~

skins.name: Hatsushimo (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Hatsushimo's retrofitting is complete. You don't think I look all that different? Oh, Commander, you're still as simple as ever~ I've changed in tons of ways beyond what's just on the surface. Heheheh~

skins.name: Ariake
skins.desc: Hatsuharu-class destroyer no. 5 - Ariake

skins.name: Unending Friendship
skins.desc: Hope everyone enjoys the oodles of balloons I made for this party! Yeah, I'm sure the little girls will love 'em!

skins.name: Ariake (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Ah... So this is what it feels like to be retrofitted. I'll work harder for your sake, and for everyone in the 27th Destroyer Division~

skins.name: Yuugure
skins.desc: Sixth ship of Hatsuharu class Destroyer— Yuugure

skins.name: Maid-In-Training!
skins.desc: "I, Yuugure the maid, shall dedicate myself to Ariake, my sister, and you, Commander!"... Eek?! M-my skirt...!

skins.name: Twilight Blossom
skins.desc: The Dragon Empery's New Year celebrations and new outfits are sure to lift everyone's spirits~ My sister will probably love this new dress as well. Commander, what do you think?

skins.name: Evening Flower
skins.desc: I finished changing, Commander. This dress is very pretty, but... isn't it missing something up top?

skins.name: Summer Festival Shopping
skins.desc: Woah... These stalls have all sorts of amazing things~ Commander, will you help me pick a gift out for Ariake? Hm, let's see... How about this Daruma doll?

skins.name: Fun in the Sun
skins.desc: I was really looking forward to playing with you at the beach, Commander, so I changed into this swimsuit. Umm... Ariake told me that I had to choose something that was easy to move around in, and cute enough to make you lose your mind... Was she pulling my leg?

skins.name: Yuugure (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Ariake-class destroyer, Yuugure, has completed retrofitting. Ehehe, from now on... Ariake and I will be in your care once more, Commander.

skins.name: Kuroshio
skins.desc: Kagerou-class destroyer number three – Kuroshio.

skins.name: Oyashio
skins.desc: Kagerou-class destroyer number four – Oyashio.

skins.name: Shimakaze
skins.desc: Shimakaze-class destroyer – Shimakaze.

skins.name: World's Speediest Bunny Waitress
skins.desc: Hippity hoppity! Grab a glass and have a sippity! Whew, I must say, this outfit was tricky to get into. Still, you made an exquisite pick, Commander!

skins.name: The White Rabbit of Wonderland
skins.desc: Whoa-whoa-whoa! Why'd I end up here again?! Even though I've been running for a whole hour! ...Commander?! Waaaah, I'm so glad to see you! Please, help me get out of heeeeeeere!

skins.name: The Island Wind Rests
skins.desc: You can't keep sprinting across the sea forever. Sometimes, you need to rest and recover your strength. Speaking of, you may use my parasol if you like, Commander!

skins.name: Kamikaze
skins.desc: Kamikaze-class destroyer number one – Kamikaze.

skins.name: Kamikaze (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Ohohoho, you must have a sharp eye if you've decided to retrofit me~ Now that I've been chosen, I cannot afford to embarrass you. Now, take a good and thorough look at this veteran's aspirations~

skins.name: Matsukaze
skins.desc: Kamikaze-class destroyer number four – Matsukaze.

skins.name: Matsukaze (Retrofit)
skins.desc: There we go... My fan is too big, and I'm not used to carrying it around yet... Ah, right, come here for a sec, Commander~ I'll fan you with some cool air~ Come on now, no need to be shy~

skins.name: Mutsuki
skins.desc: Mutsuki-class destroyer number one – Mutsuki.

skins.name: Mr. Reindeer, Depart!
skins.desc: Commander, Merry Christmas~! I am on my best behavior today as well! Uuu... when is Santa Claus going to come? I'm sleepy...

skins.name: Candy Festival!
skins.desc: Comainder, I put on my yukata just like you said! Ehehe, you should take me to the festival so I can get lots and lots of candy!

skins.name: Spring Festival Sweets
skins.desc: I heard that if I go around telling people "Happy New Year," I can get lots of goodies! Ehehe, I hope they'll give me a bunch of candy!

skins.name: Mutsuki (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Comainder, I'm done retrofitting! Have some candy! Hm? You're always nice to me, so I'm giving you some candy!

skins.name: Kisaragi
skins.desc: Mutsuki-class destroyer number two – Kisaragi.

skins.name: New Year's Wish
skins.desc: Co... commander, Kisaragi's new outfit... How does it look? It's a new year... Kisaragi wants to keep improving...

skins.name: Kisaragi (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Kisaragi... retrofitting complete... I want to be able to help everyone out more...

skins.name: Uzuki
skins.desc: The fourth ship of Mutsuki class destroyer — Uzuki

skins.name: Sleepy Uzuki
skins.desc: Ah... Big sis Kisaragi, big sis Mutsuki, let's sleep together... Commander? You want to come too?

skins.name: Minazuki
skins.desc: Mutsuki-class destroyer number six – Minazuki.

skins.name: Fumizuki
skins.desc: Mutsuki-class Destroyer number seven – Fumizuki.

skins.name: Sleepy Fairy
skins.desc: Huh...? Where am I...? What time is it...?

skins.name: Nagatsuki
skins.desc: Mutsuki-class destroyer number eight – Nagatsuki.

skins.name: Dangerous Kitty Maid?
skins.desc: Nagatsuki the kitty maid is at your service~ Do your best to not fall madly in love with my cute looks~! Hehe~

skins.name: Mikazuki
skins.desc: Mutsuki-class destroyer number ten – Mikazuki.

skins.name: Sweet Zombie
skins.desc: Mikazuki is supposed to be... a jiangshi? Um... hip... hop... Commander, trick or treaaaaat~

skins.name: Umikaze
skins.desc: Shiratsuyu-class destroyer number seven – Umikaze.

skins.name: Soft and Fluffy Therapy
skins.desc: What's the matter, Commander? Oh, this outfit? ...Um, I heard that this outfit would bring you therapeutic benefits and hoped to try it on... Wh-what do you think? Does it feel therapeutic to you?

skins.name: Baby Steps
skins.desc: Commander, it is my pleasure to accompany you today. Umm... What do you think? I decided to go for a different outfit this time... D-do you think it's cute?

skins.name: Yamakaze
skins.desc: Shiratsuyu-class destroyer number eight – Yamakaze.

skins.name: Now for a Magic Trick!
skins.desc: Voilà! Don't go anywhere, Commander! My magic show will start in just a sec! To start with, let's hear a roar! Roooaar!

skins.name: Kawakaze
skins.desc: Shiratsuyu-class destroyer number nine – Kawakaze.

skins.name: Monochromatic Interlude
skins.desc: Mhm. Lightweight clothing makes it easier to fight. Thanks, Commander... "It looks cute on me"? W-well, thanks...

skins.name: Unsullied White Fox
skins.desc: This must be the dream you've awaited so eagerly... Of course, I vowed to be with you until the end of our days. I shall take my rightful place beside you and your ideals. We are... together.

skins.name: Kiyonami
skins.desc: Yuugumo-class destroyer – Kiyonami.

skins.name: Festive Riding Hood?
skins.desc: S-sorry to keep you waiting... Yuugure and I picked out this outfit together. She said it "looked very Christmassy," but it doesn't look weird, right? ... Ugh...

skins.name: Niizuki
skins.desc: Akizuki-class destroyer number five – Niizuki.

skins.name: Harutsuki
skins.desc: Akizuki-class destroyer number nine – Harutsuki.

skins.name: A Dance for the Coming Spring
skins.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I am currently on my way to give a Kagura dance at the shrine. If you have time... would you like to come see it?

skins.name: Yoizuki
skins.desc: Akizuki-class destroyer number ten – Yoizuki.

skins.name: Sports Festival Preparations
skins.desc: It's my turn? Hold on... Umm, could you please not stare at me like that? It's... making me feel uncomfortable.

skins.name: Firecrackers and Steamed Buns
skins.desc: Mmh... Happy New Year. I'm working on hooking my friends up with these firecrackers... The bun I'm eating? I received it as a thank-you for my efforts.

skins.name: Urakaze
skins.desc: The 11th Destroyer of Kagerou class — Urakaze

skins.name: Seasonal Shogun
skins.desc: Before you raise a fuss about it, let me just tell you this - the concept of "Christmas" already existed during the Sengoku period, so there's nothing weird about putting on a Christmas outfit!

skins.name: Sengoku☆Shredder!
skins.desc: Ugh... Even though we finally got all our gear, we still need more band members... Commander! Stop complaining and come hither! From now on, you're a member of the Sengoku Shredders!

skins.name: Isokaze
skins.desc: Kagerou-class destroyer number twelve – Isokaze.

skins.name: New Year's Campaign
skins.desc: General, General, look! It's my New Year's outfit! Urakaze made it for me! Let's play a bunch of Sengoku wargames this year as well!

skins.name: Sengoku☆Smasher!
skins.desc: General! I, Isokaze, have done my utmost to prepare the equipment! Now, with Lord Urakaze's presence, our Sengoku☆War-Band is complete! Of course, you are more than welcome to join our ranks, General!

skins.name: Hamakaze
skins.desc: Tenth ship of Kagerou class destroyers, Hamakaze.

skins.name: The Honors Student
skins.desc: Learning is exciting. The joy of acquiring new knowledge, the sense of achievement from solving difficult problems... you'll understand once you try it. So, shall we study together, Commander?

skins.name: The Secret Ingredient is Love?!
skins.desc: I'm experimenting with different flavors since we're running a pop-up café... Alright! I think I'll go with this one! Strap in, Commander, because you're about to do a lot of taste-testing!

skins.name: Hamakaze (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Commander, have you been having more fun since I arrived? ... I see, that's great! Ehehe... Hamakaze, getting hyped!

skins.name: Tanikaze
skins.desc: Kagerou-class destroyer number fourteen – Tanikaze.

skins.name: Lost Girl and Labyrinth Butterfly
skins.desc: Little butterfly, little butterfly... Ya! It flew away... Hamakaze~ Hamakaze~ Where are you? Urakaze? Isokaze? We said we were going to play at the seaside. Where is everyone?

skins.name: Sparkly-Clean
skins.desc: Commander, I'm mopping the floor right now. Please watch your step, as it's quite slippery over there... Eek! Owch... I suppose I should've watched my own step... Ahaha...

skins.name: Tanikaze (Retrofit)
skins.desc: I'm Tanikaze, blowing and blustering from the mountaintop! Whoa! Butterflies? Butterflies?! Look, butterflies! For me? Thanks, Commander!

skins.name: Asashio
skins.desc: Asashio-class destroyer number one – Asashio.

skins.name: The Transfer Student Underneath the Dancing Petals
skins.desc: My name is Asashio, and I just transferred here today. Pleased to meet you... Even though I might not be able to get caught up with the course work, Mr. Kitty and I will do our best.

skins.name: Snow-Dusted Lynx Tips
skins.desc: Happy New Year, Commander. I am here to spend the New Year with you. Would you be so kind as to first help me down from here?

skins.name: Robes of Dancing Clouds
