skins.desc: Commander, thank you for coming to see me. I'm currently rehearsing my program for the Spring Festival performance. I do hope it is to your liking.

skins.name: Ooshio
skins.desc: Asashio-class destroyer number two – Ooshio.

skins.name: The Reindeer's Present
skins.desc: Merry Christmas~ Commander, we gotta go hand out presents to them destroyers~ You be Santa, I'll be yer reindeer~

skins.name: Woozy Party
skins.desc: Happy anniversary~ Today's a day to enjoy to yer heart's content, ya know? I'm just havin' fun in my own way, checkin' out cute girls from afar~ I appreciate yer concern though, Commander~

skins.name: Bringer of Fortunes
skins.desc: Should I hang this "fortune" poster here...? Oh, Commander, did ya also want a Spring Festival present from Ooshio here? Just kiddin'~ Hehe, anyway, happy Lunar New Year~

skins.name: Let's 'ave Lunch
skins.desc: Finally we're through with them mornin' classes~ Commander, would ya fancy havin' lunch with me? Heheh, yer wonderin' what I done made? You'll see for yerself soon 'nuff~

skins.name: Michishio
skins.desc: Third ship of Asashio class destroyers, Michishio.

skins.name: Fluttering Fanfare
skins.desc: Hello, Commander. Oh, you think I look good in this fluttery dress~? Thank you very much!

skins.name: Arashio
skins.desc: Asashio-class destroyer number four – Arashio.

skins.name: The Gentlest Firework
skins.desc: Looks like you found me, Commander. Hehe, want to light some fireworks with me? Spending time together should be more fun than being alone, right?

skins.name: Uranami
skins.desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number 10 – Uranami.

skins.name: Snow Vanguard
skins.desc: It's snowing...! I've finished rallying the forces... so let us advance!

skins.name: Hatakaze
skins.desc: Kamikaze-class destroyer number five – Hatakaze.

skins.name: Makinami
skins.desc: Yuugumo-class destroyer number five – Makinami.

skins.name: Time for School!
skins.desc: All right, everything looks good! I'm super excited and my batteries are fully charged! I'm heading out~!

skins.name: Kasumi
skins.desc: Asashio-class destroyer number 10 – Kasumi.

skins.name: New Year's Comfort
skins.desc: Warm and comforting clothes... Warm and comforting red bean soup... Ahh, I love New Year's.

skins.name: At School with Foo
skins.desc: Kasumi and Foo are excited about the new semester. Are you too, Commander?

skins.name: Kasumi (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Kasumi thinks that her outfit has gotten a bit breezier. Foo said the same thing.

skins.name: Hanazuki
skins.desc: Akizuki-class destroyer number thirteen – Hanazuki.

skins.name: Morning Moon, Beachside Flower
skins.desc: I've heard some say that summer is the season of cherry blossoms, lotus petals, and sunflowers, but... If you ask me, being able to leisurely enjoy the breeze with you feels pretty good too. Hehe~

skins.name: Blossoming Spring, Resplendent Moon
skins.desc: What kinds of flowers should I decorate the office with for the Lunar New Year...? Ugh, I just can't decide! Um, Commander, will you be inspecting the interior? I'll show you around! Phew...

skins.name: Naganami
skins.desc: Yuugumo-class destroyer number four – Naganami.

skins.name: Long Waves of Happiness
skins.desc: Akashi pushed me into getting this outfit, saying that it would surely make you happy, but... What do you think...?

skins.name: Long-Awaited Warmth
skins.desc: There's still some time before the banquet begins, and I'm afraid I'm feeling a little sleepy... W-would you mind if I took a nap? Thank you...

skins.name: Nestling Up for the Long Nights
skins.desc: I wanted to help you relieve some stress, so I thought I would read some folk tales to you... When I mentioned that, Akashi suggested these clothes to me... Wh-what do you think?

skins.name: Waves of Eternal Love
skins.desc: Now that the big day is here, I'm awfully nervous... I-I'll be in your care now and forever, okay?

skins.name: Suzutsuki
skins.desc: Akizuki-class destroyer number three – Suzutsuki.

skins.name: Suzutsuki, Beachside Attendant!
skins.desc: Commander, over here! We're about to start without you! Ahaha, what would you like to do, Commander? Beach volleyball? Sandcastle building? We can also go relax in the water if you'd like!

skins.name: Suzutsuki, Hanetsuki Adept!
skins.desc: I, Akizuki-class destroyer, Suzutsuki, shall not allow you to pass through these arches! Hwuh?! I missed the return again...!

skins.name: Oite
skins.desc: Kamikaze-class destroyer number six – Oite.

skins.name: Summer Dedication
skins.desc: Commander, have you also come to play on the beach? You're telling me to be careful? Hmph, what misfortune could possibly befall me from a game of watermelon splitting... Gwaah?!

skins.name: Jet Ink, Silver Quills
skins.desc: Happy New Year to you, Commander. To celebrate the season, I had these garments tailor-made for me, using traditional Dragon Empery clothes as a basis. I don't look... childish, do I?

skins.name: Kazagumo
skins.desc: Yuugumo-class destroyer number three – Kazagumo.

skins.name: After-School Melody
skins.desc: Toot~♪ Oh, Commander, did you hear me practicing my recorder? Umm, I'd appreciate it if you didn't tell the others.

skins.name: Placid Waves, Passionate Heart
skins.desc: *lick*... Oh, Commander, y-you're here for the fireworks? ...Want to watch them with me, then? I've got drinks. My ice cream? Umm... You can't have it.

skins.name: Wakatsuki
skins.desc: Akizuki-class destroyer number six – Wakatsuki.

skins.name: Slapdash Blue Sparrow
skins.desc: Oh nooo! Look out, Commander! ...Oh, phew... I'm glad I didn't mess up your clothes because of my carelessness! Please forgive me for my blunder! I'll clean the floor up right away!

skins.name: Yuubari
skins.desc: Yuubari-class light cruiser – Yuubari.

skins.name: Yuubari (Retrofit)
skins.desc: I've finally finished developing my new equipment! Since we still have time, let's go and try it out in live combat right now, Master!

skins.name: Nagara
skins.desc: First ship of the Nagara-class light cruisers, Nagara.

skins.name: Spring Breeze Leisure
skins.desc: Good evening, Commander. This room...? Ah, it's a special Dragon Empery-themed set I bought from Akashi's. It looks pretty snazzy and was on sale, so I picked it up. Ehehe~

skins.name: Isuzu
skins.desc: Second ship of the Nagara-class light cruisers, Isuzu.

skins.name: Night of Fairy Tale
skins.desc: There will be lots and lots of ghosts and spirits during Halloween... I, I’m not afraid!... say, can, can you hold my hand?

skins.name: Cozy Christmas Eve
skins.desc: Commander? I only came here to help wrap up all the presents for tomorrow, n-not because the fireplace is too cozy and I don't want to get up...

skins.name: Accidental Overheat?
skins.desc: Wooah! ...I fell down again... But at least it's cooler now... Huh? A photoshoot? Noo, don't take a picture of me~

skins.name: Charge, My Trusty Steeds!
skins.desc: W-w-woah! W-wait up! You guys are going too fast! I'm gonna fall! I'm gonna faaaaall! You're supposed to carry me in a way that doesn't give me a heart attack!! Commander, something crazy seems to have happened with my cavalry~!!

skins.name: Isuzu (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Retrofit complete! ...Umm, Commander? ...Wh-what's the matter? Do I really look that different...?!

skins.name: Yura
skins.desc: Nagara-class light cruiser number four – Yura.

skins.name: We are Succubi?
skins.desc: Uh... I think these clothes are a bit too much... Commander, I... don't look out of place in these, do I...?

skins.name: Kinu
skins.desc: I'm Kinu. If you want this demon to do your bidding, then you'd better show me what you're capable of!

skins.name: New Year's Blade Demon
skins.desc: Grr! What are you here for? Speak up. ...Oh, you just wanted to take a tour of the club activities? Sorry 'bout that, I don't like getting disturbed in the middle of this kind of training.

skins.name: Token and Ghost
skins.desc: Well? I've still got one card in my hand. If you want to win, then show me everything you've got! I will not have you disrespect me just for wearing a silly costume!

skins.name: Kinu (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Retrofit complete... Look forward to commanding the might of the demon ascended. I shall not disappoint you!

skins.name: Abukuma
skins.desc: Sixth ship of the Nagara-class light cruisers, Abukuma.

skins.name: Abukuma (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Combat retrofit complete! First Torpedo Squadron flagship, Abukuma, ready to sortie any time!

skins.name: Mogami
skins.desc: Mogami-class Heavy Cruiser no. 1 - Mogami

skins.name: Mogami (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.

skins.name: Mikuma
skins.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number two – Mikuma.

skins.name: Offerings of Floral Grace
skins.desc: Commander, may you and all our friends enjoy peace and good health... Alright, what did you think? That was a ceremonial dance I'd like to offer to everyone at the main event.

skins.name: Sendai
skins.desc: Sendai-class light cruiser number one – Sendai.

skins.name: Sendai (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Hmh. Guess I won't be needin' these bandages anymore. Commander, how about we find out how strong I've gotten... by having you take one of my punches?

skins.name: Jintsuu
skins.desc: Sendai-class No. 2 light cruiser, Jintsuu.

skins.name: The Tactician's Vacation
skins.desc: Hmm? Is it unusual? Hah. Even I require a change of pace to clear my mind every so often. Commander, why don’t you come out and get some fresh air as well?

skins.name: The Gray Wolf's Ploy
skins.desc: "Where do you think you're going so early in the morning, Little Red Riding Hood?" ...Oh, if it isn't the Commander. This might be my own little whim, but I often find myself thinking the same way as this character... If you don't mind, I'd like to hear your feedback about my acting.

skins.name: Jintsuu (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Since I've gotten used to living with you, Commander, I've decided to be more laid-back after receiving my remodel. My dance? Hehe... I can't show that to just anyone so easily.

skins.name: Naka
skins.desc: Sendai-class light cruiser number three – Naka.

skins.name: Foxy Summer Surfer
skins.desc: Ahaha! Another big one's coming~! Phew~ that felt amazing~! Ah, Commander, let's hit the waves together, shall we?

skins.name: Agano
skins.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number one – Agano.

skins.name: Christmas Eve Tease
skins.desc: Even though I'm not really into this whole "Christmas" thing, if it means I get to toy around with your heart by wearing this cute outfit of mine, then I suppose I would be interested. Hehe~

skins.name: Dating Game?
skins.desc: "Oh my, you're also out for a stroll? Hehe, my name's Agano. And what might yours be?" ...Jeez, Commander, take this more seriously. According to the setting, we just met for the first time.

skins.name: Blue Butterfly's Confession
skins.desc: The blunt approach is not my style, but I cannot have Noshiro think I only inch my way to success... Oh, I was just talking to myself, Commander. Hehe, so anyway, would you mind being my partner for tonight's party?

skins.name: Noshiro
skins.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number two – Noshiro.

skins.name: Uncharted Festival Grounds?
skins.desc: Just as I thought, this is the perfect place for watching fireworks. You came here thinking that too, didn't you?

skins.name: Xanadu's Eventide
skins.desc: Commander, what are you standing around for? Did you also need a change of pace? That makes two of us— Come, there's nothing to be afraid of here.

skins.name: Fragrance of the Eastern Snow
skins.desc: Whew... Oh, are you cold by any chance? I have some hot tea for you if you'd like. If you want someone to chat with, I'd be glad to keep you company.

skins.name: Cozy Enclave
skins.desc: Why don't you unwind for a bit before you start reflecting on the day's happenings? I'm sure it'll be far more efficient that way.

skins.name: Hold the Ice
skins.desc: Welcom...?! What are you doing here? Wait, don't leave—I was just surprised, that's all... Well, what would you like to order?

skins.name: Unwinding in the Sunshine
skins.desc: ...Take that! Heehee... Ahaha! Phew... I know you don't like admitting defeat, but I got you pretty good there. I might have tried a bit too hard, but I'm pretty sure you were the one who told me to give it my all.

skins.name: A Tale of Two Lovers
skins.desc: Receiving everyone's blessings is truly a deeply moving experience. But for now, let's set everything else aside and partake of our sweet bliss. After all, you're not just a spectator anymore– we're in this ride together, hehe~

skins.name: Sakawa
skins.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number four – Sakawa.

skins.name: The Colors of Love
skins.desc: Welcome! Heehee, you came because you were just so keen to see me, am I right? Then I've got to make you feel real welcome♪

skins.name: Furutaka
skins.desc: First ship of the Furutaka-class heavy cruisers, Furutaka.

skins.name: Furutaka (Retrofit)
skins.desc: What's wrong, Commander? Why are you staring at me like that? My body? Yes, some things seem to have gotten bigger... Want to take a look?

skins.name: Kako
skins.desc: Second ship of Furutaka-class heavy cruisers, Kako.

skins.name: Kako (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Performance upgraded, improvements complete. This way I can finally... *cough* Oh, it's nothing, Commander. I must simply be more strict with you in the future. Are you ready for your psychological examination?

skins.name: Aoba
skins.desc: First ship of the Aoba-class heavy cruisers, Aoba.

skins.name: Kinugasa
skins.desc: Second ship of the Aoba-class heavy cruisers, Kinugasa.

skins.name: Chikuma
skins.desc: Tone-class heavy cruiser number two – Chikuma.

skins.name: Myoukou
skins.desc: First ship of the Myoukou-class heavy cruisers, Myoukou.

skins.name: Nachi
skins.desc: Second ship of the Myoukou-class heavy cruisers, Nachi.

skins.name: Ashigara
skins.desc: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number three - Ashigara

skins.name: Brief Intermission
skins.desc: Phew... I finally managed to fix my dress... but I just can't seem to get used to it. Commander, how does my dress look? It's not strange, is it?

skins.name: Kaleidoscopic Summer
skins.desc: This whole "fashion coordination" concept is still a bit hard for me to wrap my head around, so I'm glad Nachi helped me pick out a swimsuit. Now, I just need to... Hey, Commander! Open your mouth! H-huh?! But this is what Nachi told me to do... is there some sort of problem?!

skins.name: Haguro
skins.desc: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number four – Haguro.

skins.name: A Blessing in Disguise?
skins.desc: Ow! That freakin' stings... Can't believe I actually slipped on the stairs and hit my foot. Just how clumsy am I? ...Oh, Commander? Uh, welcome?

skins.name: Caught By Nightfall
skins.desc: H-hey, help me out! ...No, I didn't come in here for fun. When I finished my security duty last night, I got to thinking about how I was going to give you chocolate for Valentine's and fell asleep. When I woke up, I was stuffed in this thing...

skins.name: Takao
skins.desc: First ship of the Takao-class heavy cruisers, Takao.

skins.name: Beach Rhapsody
skins.desc: Commander, even I’ll get embarrassed if you keep staring at me like that... Eh? Why did I bring a volleyball? Did you not order me to bring it?

skins.name: The Lessons of Spring
skins.desc: Practicing writing is a type of training, isn't it? Commander... do you want to sit down and write with me?

skins.name: School Romanza
skins.desc: Hmm... school life, huh? It's a fairly fresh experience for me. Would it be fine to pin my hair up like this? What do you think, Commander?

skins.name: Full Throttle Charmer
skins.desc: Ugh... S-such shameless attire... If not for Atago saying that it would benefit me to experience different things...! It looks good on me?! I, I see...

skins.name: Sakura Hanami
skins.desc: Commander, I've been undertaking countless bride training sessions in order to prepare for this day. As your bride, I won't let you down.

skins.name: Atago
skins.desc: Second ship of the Takao-class heavy cruisers, Atago.

skins.name: Summer March
skins.desc: The warm breeze that gently wraps around your skin, and delicate footsteps across the white sand... isn’t this the essence of summer? Commander, what does summer mean to you?

skins.name: Hallmarks of Winter
skins.desc: Oh my, it's begun to snow. Commander, should we find a nice, quiet place to enjoy the view?

skins.name: School Traumerei
skins.desc: Student handbook, textbooks... twin guns, torpedoes... and what else... Huh? Commander, I'm just packing my bags for school... is there anything I'm missing?

skins.name: Stunning Speedster
skins.desc: So, you want big sister to be your "fleet queen"? You got it. But you'd better give it your all out there, or else I'll be upset with you!

skins.name: Lily-White Vow
skins.desc: Commander... Ahh, from now on, shouldn't I call you "darling?" Come and hold my hand... Ah, at times like these, I just can't help but to want to eat you up, dar~ling~

skins.name: Maya
skins.desc: Third ship of the Takao-class heavy cruisers, Maya.

skins.name: Choukai
skins.desc: Takao-class heavy cruiser number four – Choukai.

skins.name: Tidy Store, Tidy Mind
skins.desc: There, that's it for the entrance... Oh welcome, Commander! I've been cleaning, so give me a moment... I'll be right with you!

skins.name: Suzuya
skins.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number three – Suzuya.

skins.name: Kumano
skins.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number four – Kumano.

skins.name: Fancy Waves
skins.desc: It's time for Kumano's sexy swimsuit debut~! Just kidding~☆ Hey Commander, just where~ are~ you~ staring~? Ahaha~♡

skins.name: PJ Poker Party
skins.desc: Now it's your turn, Commander! Which one's it gonna be~? You suuuure you wanna pick this card? ...I hear you, Suzuya! Stop tellin' the Commander what the cards are!

skins.name: One Thousand and One Nights' Wishes
skins.desc: Tadah! Get a load of my... dancer outfit! So, whaddya think? Ahaha~♡ Hey, Commander, where are those eyes wandering? Did ya see something ya like?

skins.name: Kongou
skins.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number one – Kongou.

skins.name: The Beauties of Nature
skins.desc: We must fully live in the present, whether during work or during leisure - this is my mantra. Commander, shall we go for an outing together?

skins.name: Hospital Talent
skins.desc: "Celebrity Endorsement of the Port Medical Facilities"... Hehehe, you've made a wise decision picking me. Commander, I can leave the ad shoot to you, right?

skins.name: Breezy Commute
skins.desc: It would be a shame to pass on this lovely weather, Commander. Why have a dull commute by train when you can enjoy a leisurely bicycle ride in the sunlight, hm? Heehee♪

skins.name: Hiei
skins.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number two – Hiei.

skins.name: Moonlit Cruise
skins.desc: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?

skins.name: Fragrant Red Plum
skins.desc: I have to admit, these qipaos from the Dragon Empery are quite elegant... I might sound arrogant saying this, but I feel like this outfit really brings out my charm. Hehe, wouldn't you agree, Commander?

skins.name: Beauty of the White Sands
skins.desc: We're headed for the white sands of the beach today. We all could use a breather every now and then, so let's just enjoy the sea breeze today. Hehe~

skins.name: Haruna
skins.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Haruna.

skins.name: Free Time Before Class
skins.desc: I think it's fine to enjoy school life once in a while... Hm? You wanna know what I'm listening to? Sure, if you're okay with just one earbud.

skins.name: Scarlet Innocence
skins.desc: I guess that looks right... Since Kongou chose this for me, I must trust her judgment... Um, C-Commander, would you mind helping me out? ...It's a bit hard to walk in this outfit...

skins.name: The Elegant Lotus
skins.desc: "My dear Commander, is this dress that my sisters tailored for me to your liking?" ...Okay, no, I can't do polite Hiei-speak like she can... So, anyway, h-how do I look?

skins.name: Kirishima
skins.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Kirishima.

skins.name: After-School Cannon Time
skins.desc: Commander, enjoying school life is all fine and well, but we must not forget our duty... That said, what missions are waiting for us today?

skins.name: Summery Audacity
skins.desc: Being in front of my sisters in this outfit is one thing, but it really is embarrassing to be wearing it in front of you, Commander. Um... ahem! What do you think? Since you're here, want to walk down to the beach together?

skins.name: Casual Dazzle
skins.desc: "Commander, bad luck for you, but you're just going to become another notch on my blade." Haha, just kidding, it's a joke! So, what do you think? My New Year's attire is pretty snazzy, isn't it?

skins.name: Graceful Ink Incense
skins.desc: The Lunar New Year is known for its hustle and bustle, but it's nice to just sit down with a brush and take in the smell of ink. Hey Commander, got any words you want to see rendered in calligraphy?

skins.name: Amagi
skins.desc: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi

skins.name: Wending Waters, Serene Lotus
skins.desc: Commander, are you here to pay me a visit? ...Ah, there is no need to be concerned about me. I made a promise to both you and Akagi that I would be mindful of my health.

skins.name: Hiei-chan
skins.desc: Fast Battleship, second ship of the Kongou-class Hiei.

skins.name: Amagi-chan
skins.desc: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi

skins.name: Fusou
skins.desc: First ship of the Fusou-class battleships, Fusou.

skins.name: The Celebration of Spring
skins.desc: Yamashiro said always dressing like a witch can be a bit old-fashioned, so she gave me a new outfit. That kid... Do you think it looks good on me, Commander?

skins.name: Perfect Partner?
skins.desc: Changing into leisure clothes, and waiting for the return of my beloved... Milord, I too have changed since meeting you.

skins.name: Fusou (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Milord! Thank you~ Not just for the retrofit, but for many many things. Hehe, it was the greatest of fortune for me and Yamashiro to meet you.

skins.name: Yamashiro
skins.desc: Second ship of the Fusou-class battleships, Yamashiro.

skins.name: Summer Offensive?
skins.desc: It’s just not summer without beach volleyball! Ah... Milord, you’re not playing? But I went through all this effort to pick out a swimsuit...

skins.name: Holiday Offensive
skins.desc: Merry Christmas! Milord, milord, how do I look? Is my Christmas outfit pretty? Ehehe~ Big sis also praised me today!

skins.name: Dressy Black Cat
skins.desc: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?

skins.name: Sales Clerk Offensive?!
skins.desc: Milord, Milord, welcome to the store! Yamashiro is a sales clerk today! Mhm, I'll do my best!

skins.name: Vacation Offensive!
skins.desc: Woah, even the air tastes totally different at this vacation spot! Milord, Milord, um, Akashi asked me to bottle up some of the air here for her! Want to give me a hand?

skins.name: Street Corner Offensive!
skins.desc: Uwaah! M-Milord?! I'm so, so sorry... You didn't get hurt, did you? Um... This is my school uniform. Fusou tailored it for me, hehe~ ... Awawa! I should head off to class now! See you later!

skins.name: Bridal Attack!
skins.desc: Milord, Milord, I've finished changing! What do you think, what do you think? Milord, do you like Yamashiro's dress~?

skins.name: Yamashiro (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Milord! I can do anything now~ bombardment or aerial strikes! So, the thing is, you can totally count on me, much much more, Milord! Milord~!

skins.name: Ise
skins.desc: First ship of the Ise-class battleships, Ise.

skins.name: Ise (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Planes: check! Main guns: check! Nobody can stop me now! Let's sortie right now, Commander! I'm fired up and wanna wreak some havoc on the battlefield!

skins.name: Hyuuga
skins.desc: Second ship of the Ise-class battleships, Hyuuga.

skins.name: Hyuuga (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Aviation battleship Hyuuga, sporting new powers, reporting in! Rest easy, Commander, I'll show you my true post-retrofit power!

skins.name: Nagato
skins.desc: Nagato-class battleship number one – Nagato.

skins.name: Great Fox's Respite
skins.desc: I shall be hosting the commander today. Manjuus, I beseech you to help me look my best. I am... *yawn* a bit sleepy... Urghh... what is that ruckus out there? C-Commander! When did you arrive?

skins.name: Guardian Fox's Shining Furisode
skins.desc: Perfect, you have arrived. As long as you are here, the usual moon-watching will prove to be much more enjoyable... Why don't you stay here today and rest for a while?

skins.name: Guardian Fox's Vacation
skins.desc: I heard that it is custom to play a "sport" at this kind of event, involving throwing pillows at others. Heheh, then I shall put the might of the Big Seven on display!

skins.name: Guardian Fox's Procession
skins.desc: Though this is a splendorous dress befitting the occasion, it is too different from my usual attire... Mutsu and Mikasa have nothing but praise for it? If you say so, then perhaps... I can take your word. Hehe.

skins.name: Great Fox's White Gown
skins.desc: It may be presumptuous of me, but please take care of me from now on... Is that acceptable? S-Somehow, it feels a little embarrassing... Ahaha...

skins.name: Mutsu
skins.desc: Nagato-class battleship number two – Mutsu.

skins.name: Warring States Warship
skins.desc: Commander, check it out! "Nothing can stop me!" Urakaze made it for me! Now I can play warring states with her! Heheh, you should know I'm a force to be reckoned with! Can't you come play with us? Why?

skins.name: A Maid's Mis-service?
skins.desc: Hmh? If fah foo, Fummamuh? ...*gulp*. I'm not lazing around! I'm just checking on the pastries that just came in! What are you doing here anyway? To "taste-test?" Or is there something wrong with the pastries? Why?

skins.name: Kaga(BB)
skins.desc: Tosa-class battleship number two – Kaga.

skins.name: Tosa
skins.desc: Tosa-class battleship number one – Tosa.

skins.name: Hometown Zest
skins.desc: An inspection? ...You're awfully gung-ho about your work considering how hot it is outside... Surely you wouldn't have some sort of ulterior motive?

skins.name: Musashi
skins.desc: Yamato-class battleship number two – Musashi.

skins.name: Violet Moonglow
skins.desc: "Welcome back, Master." Rather, that's what all the children at the café were saying to you when they greeted you at the door. Hehe, is this some new custom?

skins.name: Mikasa
skins.desc: Shikishima-class battleship number four – Mikasa.

skins.name: Style of the Sakura Capital
skins.desc: I found quite the nostalgic outfit when I was cleaning my wardrobe. Let's see... "Prepare to come with me on a new journey!" How do I look, Commander?

skins.name: Blossom-Viewing Season
skins.desc: It's about time for the flowers to bloom once more. Alas, how the time flies by... Ahem, Commander, let's see, would you like to go blossom-viewing with me?

skins.name: Reverence for Rest and Relaxation
skins.desc: Even I like to dress down and unwind from time to time. Oh? This is new and exciting for you? Well, you are welcome to come see more of it from now on! Hahaha!

skins.name: A Romantic Respite
skins.desc: Welcome to the Sakura Empire's pop-up café... Oh, Commander! Everyone's waiting for you. Now get your butt in here and experience the full extent of our fleet's hospitality! Don't be nervous, now! Hahaha!

skins.name: Untarnished Splendor
skins.desc: I, battleship Mikasa, from now until eternity, pledge to you my undying love and devotion. May we help each other, encourage each other, and walk side-by-side on the same path. I hope to meet your expectations, as unworthy as I may be.

skins.name: Kii
skins.desc: Kii-class battleship – Kii.

skins.name: Poolside Persuasion
skins.desc: Refreshing drinks, delicious food, warm sunshine... and a pool to beat the heat? Heh, isn't this the essence of summer?

skins.name: Suruga
skins.desc: Battleship Suruga, reporting for duty. It would seem that some threads of fate connect me to this port... No, don't mind my rambling. Please disregard that.

skins.name: Hundred Flowers' Auspice
skins.desc: Good morning, Commander. Everyone else seems to be dressed up on this day of celebration, so this shouldn't be a problem, right?

skins.name: Straightfaced Model Student
skins.desc: Oh. Fancy meeting you here... Walk to school together? Uh, sure! I know the way, so please just follow me.

skins.name: Uneventful Holiday Greetings
skins.desc: This should do it. With how unremarkable my present is, I doubt it'll make any waves when the... Ack! Commander?! Why are you here?!

skins.name: Hiyou
skins.desc: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number one – Hiyou.

skins.name: Junyou
skins.desc: Hiyou-class aircraft carrier number two – Junyou.

skins.name: Houshou
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier, Houshou.

skins.name: The Dream of the Autumn Pillow
skins.desc: While everyone slips into sweet dreams from the night's festivities, the sound of gossamer sliding off of smooth skin reaches your ears... Hehe, would you like to spend this night under the stars with me, Master~?

skins.name: Shouhou
skins.desc: First ship of the Shouhou-class aircraft carriers, Shouhou.

skins.name: Patrolling Witch
skins.desc: Waaaah! My candy! Candy is spillin’ everywhere! ...Wh-why are y’all chasin’ me? Commander, help me catch the pumpkin!

skins.name: Shouhou (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Commander, how do I look now that I've grown up? Are ya fallin' in love with me already? Mhm, ye definitely are~

skins.name: Ryuujou
skins.desc: Ryuujou-class Light Carrier - Ryuujou

skins.name: Slacking Samurai
skins.desc: *yawn*... Finally, a good night's rest... Now, to pick up where I left off on that RPG... M-m-m-milord, why are you here?! I wasn't slacking off or anything, I w-w-was just... Ughh....

skins.name: Dragon Hunter: Ryuujou's Rise
skins.desc: All right! Steady! Steadyyy! Gottem! Hahahah! Now I'll– M-Milord?! I-I'm just, umm... enjoying an after-school break!

skins.name: Ryuuhou
skins.desc: Ryuuhou-class light aircraft carrier – Ryuuhou.

skins.name: Firebird's New Year Dance
skins.desc: Commander, everyone seems to be busy with end-of-year preparations. If there is anything I can do to help, please let me know.

skins.name: Chitose
skins.desc: Zuihou-class aircraft carrier – Chitose.

skins.name: Summer Shine
skins.desc: An order of coconut milk... and grilled sausage. Mm, that should do it. ...Hm? Commander? Are you here to place an order, or to get away from the heat?

skins.name: Mosaic of Blending Colors
skins.desc: I had this outfit custom-made just for today... Do you like it, Commander? Um, that's good then... (*whispers*) Booyah.

skins.name: Chiyoda
skins.desc: Zuihou-class aircraft carrier – Chiyoda.

skins.name: Shimmering Surf
skins.desc: Hehe~ If you don't have any other plans, then your only task... is to enjoy a holiday by the sea! Commander, have you switched into vacation mode yet?

skins.name: Akagi
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier, Akagi.

skins.name: Paradise Amaryllis
skins.desc: "When you gaze long into the abyss, the abyss also gazes into you." Commander, please do not forget that when you gaze at Akagi~ *giggles*

skins.name: Plum and Snow
skins.desc: Commander will always remain by Akagi's side... Right, "Gods?" Of course... Akagi will deal with the pests.... Ahaha...

skins.name: Ruby-Laced Beauty
skins.desc: Commander, I've been waiting for you~ What a sinful one you are, to tempt Akagi like this for so long... But at long last, nobody will ever get between us again...♡

skins.name: Dawn-Phoenix's Summons
skins.desc: This banquet is my present to you... and your attendance is the greatest reward I could hope for~ Indeed, I shall not grant you leave tonight until you pass out. Ehehe... Ahahaha~♡

skins.name: Deep Crimson Poppy
skins.desc: We should send out even more invites... This is the best way to rid ourselves of those pesky vixens all at once!

skins.name: Kaga
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier, Kaga.

skins.name: Everlasting Killing Stone
skins.desc: "You only live once?" Where have I heard that saying before... Commander, are you getting excited?

skins.name: White Fox's New Year
skins.desc: One must wear appropriate attire for the New Year. What do you think, Commander? Let me hear your opinion.

skins.name: Exalted White Wings
skins.desc: This statue seems to have been inspired by the teachings of the Iris Orthodoxy. Though I am unfamiliar with this kind of art, gazing upon such majesty... fills one with a sense of piety. Commander, can you feel it as well?

skins.name: Gentle Blossom's Sigh
skins.desc: I never thought you'd end up taking such a long trip with me just to pick up a dress... Though I'm worried about leaving my sister behind at port, I suppose I should take your advice and relax a bit.

skins.name: Dusk-Simurgh's Vigil
skins.desc: What are you doing up here?! Oh, it's you. I thought you went to see my sister? ...You needed a breath of fresh air? That's all fine, but you should return to my sister soon before she does something mad.

skins.name: Sacred Blue Lily
skins.desc: "To hold one's hand and grow old together with him"... If it is to be with you, then it won't so bad.

skins.name: Souryuu
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier, Souryuu.

skins.name: The Crane Amidst the Pines
skins.desc: I tried wearing something a bit different from usual, but I'm not sure it suits me... Commander, what do you think?

skins.name: The Counselor Girl
skins.desc: Counselor girl Souryuu! Remedy the school atmosphere and correct your learning attitude, and...well, in short, I protect the discipline of the school.

skins.name: Souryuu (Retrofit)
skins.desc: If I can become stronger through this... Commander, what are you staring at? Don't you still have work to do?

skins.name: Hiryuu
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier, Hiryuu.

skins.name: After School Bullies
skins.desc: Without girl bullies, there would be no disciplinary girl. So...before sister catches me, let’s cause some mischief at school.

skins.name: Hiryuu (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Retrofit complete! Aircraft Carrier Hiryuu, reporting for duty! Hahaha! I finally got the chance to use that line! I'll be counting on you once more!

skins.name: Shoukaku
skins.desc: First ship of the Shoukaku-class aircraft carriers, Shoukaku.

skins.name: The Crane that Dances With the Wind
skins.desc: I prepared this outfit just for the occasion, so... Commander, you're not going to disappoint me, are you? Hehe~♪

skins.name: Sororal Wings
skins.desc: Hehe, this kind of work is a simple matter for me. Commander, please look forward to my performance~

skins.name: Zuikaku
skins.desc: Second ship of the Shoukaku-class aircraft carriers, Zuikaku.

skins.name: Ceremonial Crane
skins.desc: New Elite 1st CarDiv, Zuikaku, reporting for duty! Ahh, I've always wanted to give such a cool introduction! Shoukaku would definitely make fun of me if she heard it, but I wanted to try it while everyone is in a festive mood... Commander, what'd you think?

skins.name: The Wind's True Name
skins.desc: Commander, I volunteered to take this job in order to help you out, but this outfit... did it always require such a high degree of exposure...?

skins.name: Taihou
skins.desc: Taihou-class aircraft carrier – Taihou.

skins.name: Forbidden Fruit
skins.desc: You're taking so long to dress yourself, my Commander. Are you struggling to find something to match my dress? Hehe, it doesn't matter what you wear, you're always perfect to me♡

skins.name: Phoenix's Spring Song
skins.desc: Hehehe, I let Christmas and New Year's slip right by me, that I might use the Dragon Empery's Lunar New Year to capture my Commander's attentions... Oh, My Commander, won't you please enjoy the show I've prepared for you♡

skins.name: Enraptured Companion
skins.desc: Do I make a nice race queen, my Commander...? Hehe. With these proportions, and my fantastic outfit~♡ The others couldn't hope to compare with me!

skins.name: Sweet Time After School
skins.desc: Ehehe~ There is no greater bliss than being with you after classes are over, my Commander~ The kitty here seems to agree♡

skins.name: Temptation on the Sea Breeze
skins.desc: My Commander~ Do you like the location that I've chosen~? We have the entire evening to ourselves, free from the disturbance of anyone else...! Ahhh, my heart is throbbing even more vigorously than the ocean's waves~♡

skins.name: Shinano
skins.desc: Yamato-class ship number three – Shinano.

skins.name: Dreams of the Hazy Moon
skins.desc: The moonlight dims beneath hazy clouds, and the lights of the night sky begin to shine... The moon, and this sake, are both intoxicating... Will you not enjoy this fine evening with me...?

skins.name: Moonlit Chrome
skins.desc: Hnnh... Such clamors of merriment... Would this one be welcome amidst these festivities? Alas... If you so desire, how can this one refuse...?

skins.name: Akagi-chan
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier Akagi.

skins.name: Akagi μ
skins.desc: With the magicks of the Sakura Empire, changing my form like this is a trifle... Hehehe, Commander? Does this Akagi please you?

skins.name: Paradise Amaryllis
skins.desc: "When you gaze long into the abyss, the abyss also gazes into you." Commander, please do not forget that when you gaze at Akagi~ *giggles*

skins.name: Plum and Snow
skins.desc: Commander will always remain by Akagi's side... Right, "Gods?" Of course... Akagi will deal with the pests.... Ahaha...

skins.name: Ruby-Laced Beauty
skins.desc: Commander, I've been waiting for you~ What a sinful one you are, to tempt Akagi like this for so long... But at long last, nobody will ever get between us again...♡

skins.name: Dawn-Phoenix's Summons
skins.desc: This banquet is my present to you... and your attendance is the greatest reward I could hope for~ Indeed, I shall not grant you leave tonight until you pass out. Ehehe... Ahahaha~♡

skins.name: Taihou μ
skins.desc: With these clothes, and upon this stage... Ahaha... Ahahaha... Fate has ordained that my Commander shall fall for me here... Commander, please listen to the song of my love until the very end~♡

skins.name: Forbidden Fruit
skins.desc: You're taking so long to dress yourself, my Commander. Are you struggling to find something to match my dress? Hehe, it doesn't matter what you wear, you're always perfect to me♡

skins.name: Phoenix's Spring Song
skins.desc: Hehehe, I let Christmas and New Year's slip right by me, that I might use the Dragon Empery's Lunar New Year to capture my Commander's attentions... Oh, My Commander, won't you please enjoy the show I've prepared for you♡

skins.name: Enraptured Companion
skins.desc: Do I make a nice race queen, my Commander...? Hehe. With these proportions, and my fantastic outfit~♡ The others couldn't hope to compare with me!

skins.name: Sweet Time After School
skins.desc: Ehehe~ There is no greater bliss than being with you after classes are over, my Commander~ The kitty here seems to agree♡

skins.name: Katsuragi
skins.desc: Unryuu-class aircraft carrier – Katsuragi.

skins.name: Night-Illuminating Festival
skins.desc: It's– summer– festival– time–!! Uhh, well, maybe it's a bit too late for a "summer" festival, so maybe a regular festival is fine? Well, the important thing is that you have lots of fun, Commander! Because I sure as heck will!

skins.name: I-19
skins.desc: Type B1 cruiser submarine – I-19.

skins.name: Departure's Gentle Breeze
skins.desc: Aww, do I have to go to school? ... Oh, Commander! Are you here to see me off?

skins.name: Pillowy Paradise
skins.desc: So sleepy... Hey, Commandeeer? Do you wanna nap with me and my torpedo?

skins.name: Blossoming Bunny
skins.desc: I thought I'd try on this bunny costume! Hehehe, do you like it? If you think it's cute, I wanna hear you say it~

skins.name: I-26
skins.desc: Type B1 cruiser submarine – I-26.

skins.name: Deep-Sea Rabbit
skins.desc: Many secrets lie at the bottom of the ocean! Commander, let's go looking for them next time! It'll be like a field trip~ Heheh!

skins.name: Shortly Before the Fireworks
skins.desc: Commander, are you also waiting for the fireworks to start? There's still some time, so let's have a little chat!

skins.name: I-58
skins.desc: Type-B Mod 2 cruiser submarine – I-58.

skins.name: I-25
skins.desc: Type B1 cruiser submarine – I-25.

skins.name: Coral Reef Bunny
skins.desc: Hi there, Commander. Oh, this outfit? I'll be wearing it to school today. By the way, did you want to come sit in on my class?

skins.name: Sweet Wine of Celebration
skins.desc: Commander, Happy Lunar New Year. Would you like some sweet wine to celebrate? Oh, be careful not to drink too much~

skins.name: I-56
skins.desc: Type B3 Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-56.

skins.name: Wallflower in the Corner
skins.desc: School... is pretty nice. I can quietly stay in this corner and mind my own business...

skins.name: I-168
skins.desc: Kaidai Type VIa submarine – I-168.

skins.name: Festive Mood!
skins.desc: I look different from usual? That's obvious, isn't it... All right, all right, I was just giving you a hard time. We're at a festival, so we might as well enjoy ourselves!

skins.name: Akashi
skins.desc:
Repair ship Akashi
<color=#fad545>Can be built after unlocking

skins.name: Akashi's in the Red, Nya!
skins.desc: Commander, how does Akashi's new outfit look, nya? Isn't it cute? If you like it, then put a ring on it. I mean, everyone's gone out to play... if you don't help empty my inventory, I'll go broke, nya!

skins.name: The Black Cat Cometh!
skins.desc: Heheh, this is what I've been saving up for, nya~♪ A special dress that combines Gothic fashion with Sakura charm! Commander, how about those gems, nya?

skins.name: Welcome to AzurCon!
skins.desc: Ohh, it's Commander, nya. Have you come to buy Akashi's new work, nya? Today's a holiday, so go ahead and enjoy yourself, nya~

skins.name: Welcome to Sofmap!
skins.desc: Hehehe, come on in, nya! Can I help you find something, nya? Your genial and knowledgeable staff, Akashi, will gladly provide her detailed recommendations, nya!

skins.name: White Cat's Repayment
skins.desc: Commander, because of your continued patronage of my shop, I have no choice but to return the favor with my body, nya~! ...Just kidding, nya. Having that said, I really do love you, Commander. Even more than I love gems, nya~

skins.name: I-13
skins.desc: Type A Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-13.

skins.name: Kashino
skins.desc: Munition ship – Kashino.

skins.name: Hot Springs Relaxation
skins.desc: Ack... Owww... My apologies, Commander, I seem to have slipped on something... At times, it's hard to notice things I'm about to step on... Ugh...

skins.name: Maid for Mayhem
skins.desc: Hyah?! U-Umm, I can't get out... Oh, Commander?! I'm sorry! I tripped while I was cleaning, and I ended up stuck in here! Umm... What do I do now...

skins.name: Ibuki
skins.desc: Heavy cruiser – Ibuki.

skins.name: Winter Sylph's Reverie
skins.desc: Milord, it's starting to snow... If it suits you, please take shelter under Ibuki's umbrella.

skins.name: Snow on the Wind
skins.desc: This is my first time wearing Western clothes... Um, Milord! Does this outfit... suit Ibuki well...?

skins.name: Arrival of Spring
skins.desc: The Dragon Empery's "Spring Festival" is... filled with fun, liveliness, and pure jubilation. I can feel my true feelings welling up... Maybe, an environment like this would suit me pretty well...

skins.name: Tranquil Sunya
skins.desc: I'm glad you've returned, Milord. I've changed my attire in order to better carry out your order–for us to "relax together." Now then... could you please instruct me on how to proceed?

skins.name: Izumo
skins.desc: Battleship – Izumo.

skins.name: Izumo's Thousand Cherry Trees
skins.desc: You'd like to see my classical dance? Your tastes are quite refined, Commander... In that case, I'll show you the finest performance in the land!

skins.name: Kitakaze
skins.desc: Destroyer – Kitakaze.

skins.name: Celebration Conquest!
skins.desc: All the preparations are now complete... Commander, let us sally forth and conquer these festival grounds! ...But before that, can we get something to eat first?

skins.name: Night of Doves and Magic
skins.desc: Mm, preparations complete. If I keep it up, the production will surely be a great success. The doves have been on their best behavior too. Commander, what do you think about Kitakaze's magic show?

skins.name: Azuma
skins.desc: Large cruiser – Azuma.

skins.name: Soft Voice of Spring
skins.desc: Commander? Oh, I haven't quite finished changing. My hair still needs work... Sorry, would you mind waiting a bit longer?

skins.name: Lily-White Longing
skins.desc: I must be dreaming, to be able to don this white veil... Haha, though, what's more important is our life together afterwards! Commander, please look forward to the rich fruit of my bridal training~

skins.name: Hakuryuu
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier – Hakuryuu.

skins.name: Slice, Dice, and Serve
skins.desc: All righty, one freshly-sliced plate of sashimi coming right up! ...Huh? I'm coming across too aggressive? Even after I went through all this trouble for you, you still have something to nitpick about? ...Well, whatever. Enjoy your meal!

skins.name: Leberecht Maass (Z1)
skins.desc: Type 1934-class destroyer, Z1 Leberecht Maass.

skins.name: "Rebellious" Top Student
skins.desc: Because she’s the Z1, her results will of course be NO.1! Hehe, no matter where she goes, Z1-sama will always be the best!

skins.name: Z1 (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Hmm... So this is a retrofit, huh? Not bad! Rejoice once more, Commander, for no task or enemy is too daunting for the new and improved Z1!

skins.name: Z2
skins.desc: Type 1934-class destroyer – Z2 Georg Thiele.

skins.name: High-Rise, High-Style
skins.desc: Commander, I do wonder if your order to "come dressed in new clothes" was simply your way of saying "I want to see you in a casual outfit." No matter the case, I'm happy to oblige.

skins.name: Of Koi and Evening Hues
skins.desc: Being able to see you all flabbergasted makes changing into this outfit worth it. Are you going to keep standing there like a scarecrow? Come over here~ Who knows, we might even be able to see the fireworks from this spot.

skins.name: Z16
skins.desc: Type 1934A destroyer – Z16, Friedrich Eckoldt.

skins.name: Guaranteed Grand Slam!
skins.desc: Heh heh! Count your lucky stars, Commander, because you're just in time – to witness the one-and-only Z16 knock this thing right outta the ballpark!

skins.name: Z18
skins.desc: Type 1936 destroyer – Z18, Hans Lüdemann.

skins.name: Hermann Künne (Z19)
skins.desc: Type 1936-class destroyer, Z19 Hermann Künne.

skins.name: Karl Galster (Z20)
skins.desc: Type 1936-class destroyer, Z20 Karl Galster.

skins.name: Wilhelm Heidkamp (Z21)
skins.desc: Type 1936-class destroyer, Z21 Wilheim Heidkamp.

skins.name: Z23
skins.desc: Type 1936A destroyer, Z23.

skins.name: Philosophy Sensei
skins.desc: This is going to be on the exam! If you don't take thorough notes, I am going to punish you!

skins.name: Breezy Doubles
skins.desc: Haiyaaah! It's up to you, Ayanami! Oh, Commander! Are you actually keeping score? We might not be having a serious match, but that's no excuse for you to stand around and do nothing.

skins.name: Perfect Smile?
skins.desc: Welcome! A table for one today? Um... Commander, my smile doesn’t look stiff... right?

skins.name: The Banquet's Honor Student
skins.desc: Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just looking for Javelin and the others... Say, would you like to keep me company for a bit?

skins.name: Café Trainee @New Base
skins.desc: Hi, welcome! How may I serve y– It's you, Commander?! Err, well, I'm working as a trainee at this Sakura Empire-style café, you see... What do you think of this outfit?

skins.name: Serious Idol @Acting Manager?!
skins.desc: Jeez... Javelin's got what it takes, but I'm really concerned about Laffey and Ayanami. Oh well, I guess it's up to me to manage them... Commander, please don't forget to support me too.

skins.name: The Eyecatch in the Rye?
skins.desc: Commander, please help hold onto the ladder. I've almost got the book... Just a little more... All right... C-Commander?! Please don't look up!

skins.name: Schwarze Hochzeit
skins.desc: Whew... Sorry to keep you waiting. I was having a hard time deciding which outfit to wear... Ah, um... how do I look?

skins.name: Z23 (Retrofit)
skins.desc: My efficiency should be upgraded along with my performance. Paperwork, battle plans... I can handle them all! Commander, be prepared, we’ll be very busy~

skins.name: Keeper of the Comf-Fort
skins.desc: *sigh*... Taking care of Meowfficers is more work than you'd think... They're awfully needy for support units. Commander, make absolute sure you don't turn out like them.

skins.name: Upgrade Failure?!
skins.desc: N-no way... I lost the gear I worked so hard for because the upgrade failed, and now I'm completely out of gold... Ugh, I'm going to have to go farm the dungeon all over again...

skins.name: Z24
skins.desc: Type 1936A "Narvik class" destroyer – Z24.

skins.name: Festival-going Fiend
skins.desc: Come, human! The rite of festivities is upon us! Come hither, and let us revel in this foreign holiday together!

skins.name: The Devil on the Court
skins.desc: Heh heh... As expected, you couldn't even last for a second! Winning too easily takes all the fun out of it... You, the mortal over there, I'll give you the honor of being my next opponent!

skins.name: Z25
skins.desc: 1936A "Narvik" Class Destroyer - Z25

skins.name: Hot Summer's Cool Breeze
skins.desc: Even at the beach, we cannot afford to be careless! Commander, have you adequately prepared for today's activities?

skins.name: Z26
skins.desc: Type 1936A "Narvik class" destroyer – Z26.

skins.name: Sharing is Caring
skins.desc: Commander, welcome to my pad! Ah, give me a sec, let me go grab all the snacks and drinks and games!

skins.name: Z28
skins.desc: Type 1936A "Narvik class" destroyer – Z28.

skins.name: New Year Smorgasbord!
skins.desc: Commander, Happy New Year! Is there anything you'd like to do on New Year's Day? Say, why don't we try doing all of that stuff, all at once~?

skins.name: Sylvan Celebration
skins.desc: Prosit, Commander! I think these wild animals were attracted by the champagne's aroma. But they're well-behaved and like being petted. Do you want to be petted too, Commander?

skins.name: Z35
skins.desc: 1936B-class destroyer - Z35

skins.name: Projekt Kirschblüte
skins.desc: Commander, and all my fellow friends of the fleet, Happy New Year's! This time, your favorite idol Z35 will be presenting a brand new Sakura-themed collaboration, "Projekt Kirschblüte!" Everyone, thank you for your continued support!

skins.name: Z36
skins.desc: Type 1936B destroyer - Z36

skins.name: Z46
skins.desc: Type 1936C destroyer, Z46

skins.name: Her First Summer
skins.desc: The bustling beach, clamoring with waves of joyfulness... experiencing this kind of summer is a first for me, but I don't dislike it...

skins.name: Girls' Relay
skins.desc: Through the sweat and tears, striving for your goals. Rejoice in victory, sink within defeat... How fascinating, this "sports meet" may be.

skins.name: Star-Lit★Chocolate
skins.desc: Dancing beams of light, shimmering on-stage; uplifted voices, joined as one by song... Upon this unknown stage, my heart doth flutter... Yet this sensation, is quite refreshing.

skins.name: Jianzhi Fantasia
skins.desc: "Jianzhi," the art of breathing life into works of cut paper... is a world beyond my imagination. If these decorations are said to usher in blessings... are they akin to a coat-of-arms or a holy seal?

skins.name: Chronicles of the Dust Wars
skins.desc: Cast your eyes upon this bit of dust. As I was entrusted with the cleaning, I shall not allow this dust to remain. Will you also join me in this battle?

skins.name: Königsberg
skins.desc: Königsberg class light cruiser, Königsberg.

skins.name: Karlsruhe
skins.desc: Königsberg class light cruiser, Karlsruhe.

skins.name: Karlsruhe (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Königsberg-class light cruiser – Karlsruhe.

skins.name: Köln
skins.desc: Königsberg-class light cruiser, Köln.

skins.name: Köln (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Hmm... I feel like I can work even more efficiently than before. Commander, please rest assured, I will never betray your expectations.

skins.name: Leipzig
skins.desc:
Leipzig-class light cruiser, Leipzig.
<color=#fad545>Can be built after unlocking

skins.name: Storefront Training
skins.desc: Commander, ah, um... We have all new items on the menu, and they're on sale for a limited time only... P-please give them a try! Phew... Th-thank goodness, I managed to not flub it...

skins.name: Leipzig (Retrofit)
skins.desc: I feel like Fishy is a lot more capable than before, but I don't feel much different... M-maybe Fishy was the one to get a retrofit instead of me?!

skins.name: Nürnberg
skins.desc: Leipzig-class light cruiser – Nürnberg.

skins.name: Spring Wanderer
skins.desc: Since you so readily accepted my invitation to go on a vacation together, you must be planning to... Ahh, what I meant is, we can leave at any time if you're ready...!

skins.name: Magdeburg
skins.desc: M-class light cruiser – Magdeburg

skins.name: Cat Café Cleanup
skins.desc: You little...! Look what a damn mess you made! And I'm the one who's gotta clean it up now! ...Oh. Perfect timing, Commander. Could use a hand with the floor here, after what this little turd did.

skins.name: Gone Fishing
skins.desc: Here's an idea – how 'bout putting down the camera and actually enjoyin' the open sea? I'll move the swim ring so you can chill in the breeze with me!

skins.name: Emden
skins.desc: Dresden-class light cruiser – Emden.

skins.name: White-Black Partita
skins.desc: Raise your head, my darling human. O lost soul, you have three options – become Emden's meal, become Emden's prisoner... "Or become Emden's vassal. Our vassal♥"

skins.name: Moonsilver Union
skins.desc: Welcome, my darling human. Are you looking for something? If it is Emden you seek, you have already found her. "We, Emden, are before your very eyes."

skins.name: Elbing
skins.desc: Pillau-class light cruiser – Elbing.

skins.name: The Throne of Misfortune
skins.desc: As the mistress of this manor, I c-command thee to kneel... No, of course. I mean, what authority do I have to issue commands? I'm better suited to be a maid than a mistress...

skins.name: Sleepless Night's Wishes
skins.desc: Are you also having trouble sleeping, Commander? I-I thought so... It must be because I was praying for you to have sweet dreams... Look what I've done – now, neither of us can fall asleep... Urgh...

skins.name: Admiral Hipper
skins.desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Admiral Hipper

skins.name: Sunshine by the Hot Spring
skins.desc: W-well? Does this kimono look good on me? ...R-really? Duh, I know it looks GREAT on me! Who really cares what you think... C-can't be me... No, I didn't say anything!

skins.name: Blücher
skins.desc: Admiral Hipper-class heavy cruiser – Blücher.

skins.name: High-Altitude Head Over Heels
skins.desc: Heheheh☆ You're lagging behind, Commander! Pick up the pace or you'll be left behind! Just kidding~ I'll slow down for you so we can stick together!

skins.name: Prinz Eugen
skins.desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Prinz Eugen

skins.name: Unfading Smile
skins.desc: Relaxing on a float, gently licking my lips... is this really the most popular photo pose for the beach? Wales, you’re not teasing me again, are you?

skins.name: Profusion of Flowers
skins.desc: So this is the Sakura Empire's New Year? Hehe, how interesting~ Commander, since it's the New Year, why don't you put aside all those papers and have a drink with me?

skins.name: Cordial Cornflower
skins.desc: ... Huh? Commander, is that you? Me, drunk? No way... *hic*... If I was, Commander, then what are you planning to do to me? Hehe...

skins.name: Final Lap
skins.desc: Viel Glück~ Are you having a good time, Commander? Just know that the only person I'm cheering for... is you~

skins.name: Kindred Evening Spirits
skins.desc: Guten Abend~ So, what do you think? Pretty great view, right? Hehe, I was talking about the night scenery outside, you know~?

skins.name: Symphonic Fate
skins.desc: If fate brought us together, then it has my thanks… I look forward to our future together~

skins.name: Deutschland
skins.desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser, Deutschland.

skins.name: Dark Demon Princess
skins.desc: For a servant, your eyes are good... *coughs*... I'm an Ironblood Princess, the Queen of Night, Deutschland! Servant? No. I am the first of my family. Come, kiss the ring of royalty!

skins.name: Service Time?!
skins.desc: One must not neglect sunscreen during the summer... Plebeian, if you wish to serve your master, prostrate yourself and yell "I beg of you, Queen Deutschland" three times, and I might consider giving you an opportunity. Ahahaha~

skins.name: Demon Princess' Dark Hour Banquet
skins.desc: I seem pleased? Of course I am. Why wouldn't I be when my sweet little sister will be joining us at the party? Now shape up and entertain your master, you lowly animal! Ahahahaha!

skins.name: Lantern-Lit Ruler
skins.desc: Why are so many people out and about during a holiday? ...That's it! Lowly animal, was it your idea to prepare all this to surprise me...?! Heh... Hehe, that's right, don't you dare disappoint me!

skins.name: Admiral Graf Spee
skins.desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser number three – Admiral Graf Spee.

skins.name: Girl's Sunday
skins.desc: I sailed alone, fought alone, and then I was sunk while being alone. Now I found a new beginning... Hmm? Commander, you've been staring and laughing at me since the beginning… do you want to eat this?

skins.name: Peaceful Daily Life
skins.desc: I never dreamt that I'd be able to don this outfit and live a normal, peaceful life... Thank you, Commander...

skins.name: A Novel Anniversary
skins.desc: It's so fancy, so formal... Is this a "party"? I'm not sure I'll be able to fit in... But if you'll go with me, Commander, I'll give it a try!

skins.name: World's♥Cutest
skins.desc: My sister just wouldn't stop bugging me, so I finally caved and agreed to do this... Anyways, all I have to do is get up on stage and sing, right?

skins.name: Admiral Hipper μ
skins.desc: Huh? Why are you staring at me like I'm some weirdo? I'll have you know, it's not like I wanted to do this or anything!

skins.name: Sunshine by the Hot Spring
skins.desc: W-well? Does this kimono look good on me? ...R-really? Duh, I know it looks GREAT on me! Who really cares what you think... C-can't be me... No, I didn't say anything!

skins.name: Roon μ
skins.desc: Heavy cruiser Roon, reporting for idol activities and associated experimental equipment testing. Today, we fight not with fire and sword, but with the power of song.

skins.name: Dark Red Grin
skins.desc: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...

skins.name: Viridescent Lullaby
skins.desc: It's so nice getting away from the bustling party hall and being alone with you, Commander. I'm eager to see what we'll do now as your idea of a... "break"~

skins.name: Prinz Heinrich
skins.desc: P-class armored ship – Prinz Heinrich.

skins.name: Fireworks and Tapestries
skins.desc: Phew... Changing into these clothes took quite a long time~ So, how does it look? A fine mixing of different cultures, wouldn't you agree? Ahaha, Happy New Year, Commander!

skins.name: Rabbit on Watch
skins.desc: *ptwee*! Remember: safety first! Commander, you've got to do your stretches before going in the pool! Be thorough, or I'll get mad at you!

skins.name: Secret Boss o' the Underworld?
skins.desc: Listen up, Commander! I'm the one in charge of this school's seedy underbelly here at this port, so you'd better do what I tell you to! In return, I'll offer you my protection! Ahaha~♪

skins.name: Prinz Adalbert
skins.desc: P-class armored ship – Prinz Adalbert

skins.name: After-Hours Service
skins.desc: Zzz... Huh? Did I doze off? I just meant to rest my eyes for a sec after closing up, but look how long I slept... Hang on, why are you still here, Commander?

skins.name: Yorck
skins.desc: Roon-class armored cruiser – Yorck.

skins.name: Breaker under the Blood Moon
skins.desc: "Foolish, pitiable creature. Kneel before your Goddess!" Heehee! Hahahah, ahahahaha♥ You're the Commander, silly. You don't need to play along unless you want to.

skins.name: Little Prinz Eugen
skins.desc: Admiral Hipper-class heavy cruiser – Prinz Eugen.

skins.name: Little Spee
skins.desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser – Admiral Graf Spee.

skins.name: Scharnhorst
skins.desc: Scharnhorst-class battlecruiser, Scharnhorst.

skins.name: Panther und Pflaume
skins.desc: A festival, huh? Going for days without fighting is boring, not to mention not my style. C'mon, Commander, isn't there *something* exciting I can do during this "Lunar New Year" festival?

skins.name: Gneisenau
skins.desc: Scharnhorst-class battlecruiser, Gneisenau.

skins.name: Nightmarish Succubus
skins.desc: These Halloween festivities are quite interesting, in a good way. Getting dressed up in these costumes isn't such a bad experience either. Commander, what do you think of my costume?

skins.name: Seydlitz
skins.desc: Battlecruiser – Seydlitz.

skins.name: Heir of the Vampire Killer
skins.desc: There it is – Dracula's Castle, brought into this world by chaos itself... On my honor, I swear I will put an end to the divine bloodline!

skins.name: Floral Liberation
skins.desc: How do I look, Commandant? I thought you may like seeing me in a dress, however I don't know if this is what you desired or not...

skins.name: Lützow
skins.desc: Derfflinger-class battlecruiser – Lützow.

skins.name: Everlasting Blood Banquet
skins.desc: "Have you come to accept your fate, human? Heehee~" ...Don't just stand there, Commander. Say something!

skins.name: Steaming-Hot Treat
skins.desc: Om, nom... Hmm. Hey! This is pretty good! I mean, of course it's good – it's Empery cuisine! Commander, open wide and I'll give you a dumpling alley oop. Say "aah"!

skins.name: Brünhilde
skins.desc: O-class battlecruiser – Brünhilde.

skins.name: Grain-Seizing Grani
skins.desc: Hah! This donut now belongs to Brünhilde! Alright, now for the finish line... C-Commander? Sorry, but there's no time for chit-chat... I'll be going now!

skins.name: Bismarck
skins.desc: Bismarck-class battleship – Bismarck.

skins.name: Beacon of the Iron Blood
skins.desc: My sincerest apologies for the delay, Commander. Ah, excuse me... as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood, I'm expected to wear this outfit to various formal occasions. Just putting it on seems to make me inadvertently change the way I speak...

skins.name: Iron-Black Elysium
skins.desc: Welcome, what would you like to order? ...If you want, we can drop this charade. I'm not used to being a waiter anyway, so I prefer it this way. Hehe.

skins.name: Tirpitz
skins.desc: Bismarck-class battleship, Tirpitz.

skins.name: Snow-Melting Summer
skins.desc: Summer... In the past, it was always just a hot and stifling season... But now...? Doesn't my outfit tell the whole story? Let's get going, there's bound to be a lot of people on the beach.

skins.name: Iron Blood Snowstorm
skins.desc: I bet Bismarck must've been thinking about how to invite me to the party, but ended up asking you to do it, Commander. Hehe... Let's get going soon. It's best not to keep her waiting.

skins.name: Seasonal Pine and the Frost Flower
skins.desc: They have a peculiar way of wishing a happy New Year in the Sakura Empire. In line with their traditions, I've put on this new outfit. I hope it doesn't... look strange on me. ...You like it? I see... That being the case, I'll keep wearing it for the time

skins.name: A Vase for the Frost Flower
skins.desc: It's all right, I just got here myself. I will say, it's strangely reassuring to know I'm not the only one nervous on this day.

skins.name: Ulrich von Hutten
skins.desc: H-class battleship – Ulrich von Hutten

skins.name: Mayhem Maid
skins.desc: *sigh* Do you really have to bother me during my break? ...It's a joke, no need to take it so seriously. I was looking for someone to kill some time with anyway.

skins.name: Thüringen
skins.desc: Helgoland-class battleship – Thüringen.

skins.name: Tidying in the Moonlight
skins.desc: You, mop the floor. You, take care of the windows. Once that's done... Ah, Commander. Excuse us, we're in the middle of cleaning the area. If you have need of me, I must ask you to wait.

skins.name: Weser
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier – Weser.

skins.name: Obsidian Elegance
skins.desc: I've been waiting for you, Comander. As per my sister's recommendation, I've put on this Sakura Empire kimono. It was very tricky to get into, I might add... That aside, how do I look? ...Good enough, I hope?

skins.name: Urbane Onyx
skins.desc: Ah, I've kept you waiting. I do apologize that it took so long to get changed into this outfit. Now, Commander, won't you come show me your chivalry and escort me down these stairs?

skins.name: Wave-Washed Paradise
skins.desc: I've been waiting forever for this season to arrive. It's a perfect time, the waves wait for nobody, so I'm off for now. I'll make sure to teach you how to surf later, so look forward to it.

skins.name: Elbe
skins.desc: Jade-class aircraft carrier – Elbe

skins.name: Time to Show Off?
skins.desc: Thank you all for waiting! Large mugs of Iron Blood beer, just as ord–– W-waaah?! Nnngh...! Phew, somehow managed to not spill anything... Wh-what's your deal?!

skins.name: Pure-Hearted Bad Girl
skins.desc: Still not here yet...? Geez, I'll give the Commander what-for for coming later than me... Huh? C-Commander? N-no, I happened to come an hour early, is all...

skins.name: Graf Zeppelin
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier, Graf Zeppelin.

skins.name: Beachside Urd
skins.desc: So the Second Movement is a Lento of the summer and the sea? So be it... Since we will arrive at the Finale eventually, I suppose I can enjoy this moment of fleeting peace with you.

skins.name: Zeppy
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier Graf Zeppelin

skins.name: Peter Strasser
skins.desc: Graf Zeppelin-class aircraft carrier – Peter Strasser.

skins.name: Chronos's Kalendae
skins.desc: Eugen, you said that this was is a ceremonial outfit from the Sakura Empire? Surprisingly, it does seem to suit me rather well. Oh, I'm supposed to offer my well-wishes for the New Year at this time, yes?

skins.name: A Moment Frozen in Pure White
skins.desc: You already know, don't you? Since I spent so much of my precious time changing into a dress for your sake... Heh, I'll be taking plenty of your time in return. Hehehe.

skins.name: U-81
skins.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-81.

skins.name: Soft Serenade
skins.desc: *Ugh*... I figured this bulky dress would be hard to move in... Huh? I look pretty? Aha, ahaha... You're makin' me blush...

skins.name: Lantern-Lit Full Moon
skins.desc: Over here, Commander! I came because you said we were going to go moon-viewing together! I even brought tea and mooncakes.

skins.name: U-47
skins.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-47.

skins.name: Rookie Rider
skins.desc: I haven't seen much of the world on land... Commander, want to explore it with me?

skins.name: Eigenen Raum
skins.desc: Sigh... I'd much rather be in a nice, quiet place like this over the din and clamor of the venue... Wouldn't you agree, Commander? I see. Well, come sit here then.

skins.name: Urban Maid
skins.desc: Coming through! Steer clear! Oh, it's you, Commander. Talk to you later – I've got coffee to deliver.

skins.name: Sanguine Moon Sojourn
skins.desc: An empty study with a cushy couch. The perfect place to relax. Whew... Go ahead and read a book if you want, Commander. If that'll be all then I'm gonna take a nap.

skins.name: Hook, Line, and Sinker
skins.desc: Nice. I've found a legendary luck-bringing carp, like... Oh. I almost had it, too... Sorry, Commander.

skins.name: U-557
skins.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-557.

skins.name: U-556
skins.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-556.

skins.name: Party Knight!
skins.desc: It's me, U-556, all prettied up! Eheheheh, we're gonna have lots of fun at this party, Commander! Come on, let's go!

skins.name: U-73
skins.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-73.

skins.name: Science Rules!
skins.desc: It's time for science class with U-73! Now, Commander, let's try out an exhilarating and positively fascinating experiment!

skins.name: New Year's Chemistry
skins.desc: In today's chemistry lesson, we'll learn how to make a warming cup of tea and an optional concoction to enhance its flavor! Will you do the honor of taste-testing it, Commander?

skins.name: U-101
skins.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-101.

skins.name: Ironbrass Trombonist
skins.desc: Commander, welcome to the school band! Why'd I join the band? The reason's simple - there's no Motorbike Club at school, haha! Just kidding~! Actually, I'm quite fond of music as well, heh.

skins.name: U-522
skins.desc: Iron Blood Type IXC submarine – U-522.

skins.name: U-110
skins.desc: Raaaawr. U-110 is a shaaaark. Fear meeee. Mess with me and I'll bite yooouuu.

skins.name: Kleiner Hai
skins.desc: Whenever I play games with Bulldog, I always end up losing. Frustratinggg. That's why... I'll study hard. One day, I'll winnnn.

skins.name: A Cute, Sharky Reverie
skins.desc: I have to wear beautiful clothes to a party, or so Bulldog said. So, I had everyone help me pick out beautiful clothes. Commander, I'm beautiful, right? Eh... cute?

skins.name: Garnished Supershark
skins.desc: The horned idol U-110 splashes onto the staaage. I'll sing all the baddies to obliviooon. I'm scaaary. Raaawr. Raaawr♪

skins.name: New Year, Small Shark
skins.desc: Commander, happy new yeeear. I'm no bunny, I'm a shaaark. Not a cute shark, but a crimson, scaaary shark. Raaawr.

skins.name: Springtime Shark
skins.desc: I'm gathering mushrooms, not garlic cloooves. The edible ones are gonna go in a hearty hot pot that'll warm me and my frieeends. Raaawr.

skins.name: U-96
skins.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-96.

skins.name: Secret Gaming Session
skins.desc: Nice timing. I just finished an intense battle. The result...? Of course I won. What? Did you want to have a match against me?

skins.name: How Heavy Are Those Barbells?
skins.desc: Mmgh... Guh... Ahhh! These things are heavier than they look... Oh, there you are. You work out too, do ya? Feel free to join me if you've not just come to tease me.

skins.name: U-37
skins.desc: Iron Blood Type IXA submarine – U-37.

skins.name: New Year's Nightingale
skins.desc: Now then, please lend your ears to this song I shall offer you... Wait, Commander, are you spacing out again? Even though I went through all this trouble to learn this song from my friends in the Sakura fleet... Please pay attention, okay? I'm starting ov

skins.name: U-410
skins.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-410.

skins.name: Spring Festival Scheme
skins.desc: Happy Lunar New Year. Have you cooked up a scheme for this year's festival? Hehehe~ I'm of course talking about giving out New Year's gifts and hanging up decorations. I've devised a master plan of my own.

skins.name: U-1206
skins.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-1206

skins.name: Maid Just for You
skins.desc: Welcome! Oh, Hey, Commander! Heheh, so how do you like my maid getup? Looks pretty nice, if I do say so myself!

skins.name: Roon
skins.desc: Heavy cruiser – Roon.

skins.name: Dark Red Grin
skins.desc: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...

skins.name: Viridescent Lullaby
skins.desc: It's so nice getting away from the bustling party hall and being alone with you, Commander. I'm eager to see what we'll do now as your idea of a... "break"~

skins.name: Friedrich der Große
skins.desc: Battleship – Friedrich der Große.

skins.name: Dark Raiments of Gagaku
skins.desc: I see, so this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire. Exquisitely crafted, comfortable to the touch, and elegantly designed... How to wear it? ...My child, what are you talking about?

skins.name: Zeremonie of the Cradle
skins.desc: Ahh, the dreamlike beauty of this variation... let us write down this movement so that it may continue forever, my sweet child.

skins.name: Mainz
skins.desc: Light cruiser – Mainz.

skins.name: Odin
skins.desc: Battlecruiser – Odin.

skins.name: Black Strokes upon Blank Snow
skins.desc: I thought I would never have time to pursue the fine arts, and yet here I am now. Your thoughts, Commander? Eastern as this calligraphy may be, does it not suit the connotations of my name?

skins.name: Ägir
skins.desc: Large cruiser – Ägir.

skins.name: Iron Blood's Dragon Maid
skins.desc: Hmph. They think being a maid is so difficult, do they? I could do this with my eyes clo– What?! H-how long have YOU been here?!

skins.name: Golden Dragon Among Auspicious Clouds
skins.desc: New decorations, new outfits, and countless preparations to make... Lunar New Year is quite the busy time of year. Go on, see to your duties. I'm well aware how essential you are to this holiday's smooth operation. Just don't keep me waiting all day. Heehee.

skins.name: August von Parseval
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier – August von Parseval.

skins.name: The Conquered Unhulde
skins.desc: My hair is a mess... There we go. No, I don't need a hand. I am here to serve you in this fleeting dream of yours. Enjoy it while it lasts. Hehehe.

skins.name: Prinz Rupprecht
skins.desc: Battlecruiser – Prinz Rupprecht.

skins.name: The Gate Dragon's Advent
skins.desc: Woah, so this is the Dragon Empery's "Spring Festival" that I've heard so much about. But, why are they celebrating it in the middle of winter? And you, Commander – why are you helping with such a grandiose... Whuah?! What was that noise?!

skins.name: An Shan
skins.desc: An Shan-class destroyer, No. 1 - Anshan (101)

skins.name: Setting Sun, Hearts as One
skins.desc: "Boundless is the beauty of evening's glow, but alas––" ...Oh, that doesn't have any special meaning, I've just been hanging around Hai Tien too much. (*whispers*) But, it's true... Our time together is far too short, just like the evening light...

skins.name: An Shan (Retrofit)
skins.desc: An Shan, retrofitting complete! With this new power, Commander, I'll protect both you and my sisters! But first... Umm, I need to double-check how these missiles work...!

skins.name: Fu Shun
skins.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No.2 - Fu Shun (102)

skins.name: The Unbreakable Baozi Heist
skins.desc: Heh-hey! Just hooked us another baozi~! We're in for one heckuva haul today! ...Eh? Huh, Commander?! Th-this is, uhh... yeah, we're just playing a normal game... totally...

skins.name: Chang Chun
skins.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No. 3 - Chang Chun (103)

skins.name: The Joy of Spring
skins.desc: Ta-da! My pajamas are finally finished! Now to snuggle up until I'm all warm! Eh~ Ehhh? But sis, I don't want to get out! Ack, did Tai Yuan purposely make this tail big and thick to make it easier for you?

skins.name: Fortune Arrives in Red
skins.desc: Commander, hurry up and plug your ears! Th-this isn't a joke! Um... Seriously, that big ol' doozy over there is about to blow!

skins.name: Chang Chun (Retrofit)
skins.desc: All done with my retrofit~ Now, time to test out my new toys... Err, I mean, time to test the firepower of my new armaments! Oh, watch your head, Commander! Wouldn't want one of the missiles to lock onto you.

skins.name: Tai Yuan
skins.desc: An Shan-class destroyer No. 4 - Tai Yuan (104)

skins.name: The Golden Dragon's Festivities
skins.desc: O-on behalf of the An Shan class, we wish a prosperous, happy, and healthy new year to Commander, and to everyone here at port... Umm... even though I made this outfit, I feel a bit embarrassed wearing it... Eh? It looks good on me? Um... th-thank you...

skins.name: Yat Sen
skins.desc: Cruiser, Yat Sen.

skins.name: Paragon of Celestial Grace
skins.desc: I am truly honored to be able to share this wondrous scenery with you on such a festive occasion, Commander. Umm... I'm not just saying that out of courtesy. We rarely get opportunities like this, so I'm somewhat flattered...

skins.name: Coronal Afterglow
skins.desc: Commander, thank you for waiting for me. Though I am unworthy of this honor, thank you so much...

skins.name: Yat Sen (Retrofit)
skins.desc: There's no need to worry, Commander. I will be fine now. Please allow me to serve you once more in this new form.

skins.name: Ning Hai
skins.desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruiser, Ning Hai

skins.name: Summer Hunger
skins.desc: Summer’s all about the beach! And the beach is all about good food! Commander, let’s find something delicious to eat!

skins.name: Moon Palace Rabbit
skins.desc: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival! I heard that if you pray to the moon today, you’ll become as pretty as the Goddess of the Moon! ...Eh? You’re gonna pray too?

skins.name: Dragon Sisters! -N
skins.desc: We haven't had to worry as much about things like food since we joined the fleet, but that doesn't mean we can just throw money around...! Anyway, I'm the older of the "Dragon Sisters," Ning Hai! Great to be here!

skins.name: Springtime Sojourn
skins.desc: Commander, what are you spacing out for? Over here! They say that you'll have good fortune if you give this thing a shake!

skins.name: Gorgeous Violet
skins.desc: Yat Sen said this look would be best for a party, but, is it really okay? I'm not used to having my hair down like this...

skins.name: Da Bao's Friend!
skins.desc: Good boy. Chew thoroughly before you swallow. I never thought I'd help with a charity event for nature, but Da Bao's made a lot of new friends because of it. Keep up the good work, Commander and Ping!

skins.name: Ning Hai (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Yes! … this feels good. Thank you, Commander. In order to live up to your expectations, from now on, I will be more serious around you, Commander. Hey, don't run!

skins.name: Ping Hai
skins.desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruser, Ping Hai

skins.name: Summer Vacation
skins.desc: Compared to pork buns, shaved ice is tastier. Compared to shaved ice, fireworks are prettier. Compared to fireworks, what I care for the most is...

skins.name: Osmanthus Moon Rabbit
skins.desc: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander! Mooncakes, pomegranates, and osmanthus cakes... what a wonderful holiday!

skins.name: Dragon Sisters! -P
skins.desc: Big sister says that even though we have some money now, we still have to save as much as we can. Um... Anyway, I'm the younger "Dragon Sister," Ping Hai. Erm... I'm kind of hungry. Do you maybe have something to eat?

skins.name: Great Gourmet Expedition
skins.desc: The Sakura Empire has lots of delicious food that I've never tried before! Yeah! It's a great place!

skins.name: Delicious Crimson
skins.desc: There's always a lot of delicious food at these parties! But, my sister said I'm not allowed to have any cake until everyone's gotten their slice... Baobao, let's be on our best behavior!

skins.name: Baobao's Buddy!
