skins.desc: Cheese! That came out looking good! Hehehe~ I'm really glad to be a part of this charity event for nature, along with you and my sister! Baobao is really glad too!

skins.name: Ping Hai (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Hi~ya! Hmm... this feels... nothing special. Baobao looks happy though... Never mind, Commander, Ping Hai is hungry!

skins.name: Ying Swei
skins.desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Ying Swei.

skins.name: Snowy Pine's Warmth
skins.desc: Happy New Year, Commander. I've come to deliver you blessings for this coming year... Next, you're going to ask for a red envelope, right? Hehe, just teasing~

skins.name: Frolicking Flowers, Verse I
skins.desc: Commander, Happy New Year! Chao Ho and I are preparing for this year's Spring Festival, and as you can see... we're in the middle of a little "intermission." Hehe, don't worry, there's nothing you need to help out with. Just take a seat over there and enjoy the show~

skins.name: Chao Ho
skins.desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Chao Ho.

skins.name: Plum Blossom's Illumination
skins.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! This red envelope is my gift to you... after all, that's my responsibility as a big sister! Anyway, hurry up and take it!

skins.name: Frolicking Flowers, Verse II
skins.desc: Happy... New Year... Commander... Gah, this isn't the time for pleasantries! And you, help me catch the dumb fluffball that ran off with our ornaments! Jeez, why is this happening when I'm in the middle of getting ready for the Spring Festival?!

skins.name: Hai Tien
skins.desc: Hai Tien-class protected cruiser – Hai Tien.

skins.name: Verse-Weaver at the Water's Edge
skins.desc: What a serendipitous meeting this is, Commander. I was simply searching for a place where I could leisurely enjoy my poetry manuscript. Since fate has brought both of us here, why don't we accompany each other for a while?

skins.name: Hai Chi
skins.desc: Hai Tien-class protected cruiser – Hai Chi.

skins.name: A Dance Among the Lotuses
skins.desc: Look, Commander! I've become a goddess from the Dragon Empery's folklore! Hehehe! Let me perform for you a song and dance number I just learned!

skins.name: Chen Hai
skins.desc: Seaplane carrier - Chen Hai.

skins.name: Vestibule of Wonders
skins.desc: You're here, Commander, just as promised. How do you like the atmosphere in here? Hehe, take a seat and enjoy the tea slowly. After all, we have plenty of time~

skins.name: Cerulean Ripples
skins.desc: Oh my, if it isn't the Commander... Have you also come to escape the heat? What a serendipitous meeting... Or, did you perhaps have some other goal in mind? Heehee...

skins.name: Hwah Jah
skins.desc: Seaplane carrier – Hwah Jah.

skins.name: The Festive Undead
skins.desc: I am Hwah Jah, now in zombie form. It is an honor to see you– hmm? What's wrong, Commander? Everyone else is getting dressed up for the occasion, so I figured I'd get in on the action too... Is there something wrong with that?

skins.name: Ting An
skins.desc: Seaplane carrier – Ting An.

skins.name: Tender White Jade
skins.desc: I see, so this is how you're supposed to knead dough... Hmm? Commander? As you can see, I'm currently trying to make baozi. Would you like to help out?

skins.name: Harbin
skins.desc: Light cruiser - Harbin.

skins.name: Union Between Sea and Sky
skins.desc: Pheeew! I just love blue skies and a fair ocean breeze. Since you're already here, Commander, set aside all the boring paperwork and business stuff, and come enjoy the waves!

skins.name: Carabiniere
skins.desc: Soldati-class destroyer – Carabiniere.

skins.name: Refreshing Sundress
skins.desc: Lady Veneto advised me to enjoy my time off by changing into something befitting the occasion... Um, Commander, I d-don't look strange, do I?

skins.name: Vincenzo Gioberti
skins.desc: Alfredo Oriani-class destroyer – Vincenzo Gioberti.

skins.name: Fair Lady's Invitation
skins.desc: "To refuse a fair signorina's invitation would be most uncouth"... Hehe~ Now, Commander, would you like to partake in some refreshments? Rest assured, they're all non-alcoholic♪

skins.name: Maestrale
skins.desc: Maestrale-class destroyer – Maestrale.

skins.name: Lonesome Beachfarer
skins.desc: It's way too crowded on the beach... I'd much rather be– Oh, Commander? Are you not good with crowded places either...?

skins.name: Libeccio
skins.desc: Maestrale-class destroyer – Libeccio.

skins.name: Beachbound Southwestern Wind!
skins.desc: Libeccio's heading towards the sea! Commander, let's go to where all the excitement is!

skins.name: Nicoloso da Recco
skins.desc: Navigatori-class destroyer – Nicoloso da Recco.

skins.name: To a Smashing Voyage!
skins.desc: I know this one! It's that Sakura Empire watermelon-smashing game! Just put the melon over there, Commander! ...Relax, it'll be fine! Have some faith in my navigator's intuition! Ready? Then let's go!

skins.name: Pompeo Magno
skins.desc: Capitani Romani-class ship – Pompeo Magno.

skins.name: Quaver Daydream
skins.desc: *yawn*... Nothing's impossible when you've got Captain Pompey... Hmm? Commander? Wait, I fell asleep? Seems I did... Drat, I forgot what I even came here for...

skins.name: Alfredo Oriani
skins.desc: Oriani-class destroyer - Alfredo Oriani.

skins.name: Vivacious Vivace
skins.desc: Found you, Commander! How would you grade this outfit of mine? ...No, no, I wasn't asking if it looked cute or pretty, I wanted to know if I was wearing it right in the first place! You know what though, I think I'll take those compliments~

skins.name: Emanuele Pessagno
skins.desc: Navigatori-class destroyer – Emanuele Pessagno.

skins.name: Backstage Blunders
skins.desc: Eek! Wh-why are you guys tugging at my stockings... P-please stop that... C-Commander, please... Hurry and come help me! Waah...

skins.name: Duca degli Abruzzi
skins.desc: Duca degli Abruzzi-class light cruiser – Luigi di Savoia Duca degli Abruzzi.

skins.name: Lustrous Onyx Sirenetta
skins.desc: Good evening, Commander. Here to unwind after a day's work, I take it? Even dignitaries desire a bit of luxury sometimes. Hahaha.

skins.name: Giuseppe Garibaldi
skins.desc: Duca degli Abruzzi-class light cruiser – Giuseppe Garibaldi.

skins.name: Noble Ivory Plumes
skins.desc: I am the evil swan Odile! Where oh where is my prince? ...Oh, it's you, Commander. My lines aside, pretty good performance, right?

skins.name: Trento
skins.desc: Trento-class heavy cruiser – Trento.

skins.name: Summer's Hotness?
skins.desc: The summer's scorching heat is alleviated by the ocean~ Commander, why don't you set aside your worries and... cut loose a bit~?

skins.name: Zara
skins.desc: Zara-class heavy cruiser – Zara.

skins.name: Poolside Coincidence
skins.desc: Phew... It's a perfect day for swimming. Oh my, Commander, did you come to swim too? Or... perhaps you had something else in mind? Ehehe~♪

skins.name: Pola
skins.desc: Zara-class heavy cruiser – Pola.

skins.name: Seaside Coincidence
skins.desc: Zara, how dastardly of you to spike the ball at such a time– Eek?! Commander?! Why are you in a place like that?

skins.name: Trieste
skins.desc: Trento-class heavy cruiser – Trieste.

skins.name: Rooftop Lunch Break
skins.desc: Oh my, are you done with your errands already? Surely, you didn't skip work just to eat lunch with... Ah, sorry for doubting you. Alright, let's go. Trento is waiting for us.

skins.name: Bolzano
skins.desc: Heavy cruiser – Bolzano.

skins.name: A Flutter in the Moment
skins.desc: I've never had a knack for dancing or exercise unlike Zara and her sisters... but if asked, I will dance as best as I can! Please keep your eyes on me, Commander!

skins.name: Tempting Treasure
skins.desc: So... The premise is that you and I were shipwrecked and ended up on a desert island... Is that right, Commander? I see... But if we weren't actually shipwrecked... what is this treasure, then?

skins.name: Vittorio Veneto
skins.desc: Vittorio Veneto-class battleship – Vittorio Veneto.

skins.name: The Flower of La Spezia
skins.desc: Nngh, haah... It's awfully sunny today... How long was I asleep, Commander? Oh, it's already lunchtime? In that case, I'll get started on some food. Would you like something as well?

skins.name: Littorio
skins.desc: Vittorio Veneto-class battleship – Littorio.

skins.name: The Glory of Naples
skins.desc: A visit to the beach with me? Then you must try your hardest to stand out. Otherwise the eyes of the world will be on me alone.

skins.name: Calabria Aurea
skins.desc: Welcome to Littorio's personal suite. Are you here to issue me a challenge of who can romance the most girls? Hahahah, I'm joking of course! There'd be no fun in a game I would win every single time.

skins.name: Lounging Emerald
skins.desc: Hello there. You'll have to forgive the loungewear; I have scarcely any reason to wear extravagant clothes in my private space away from the public eye.

skins.name: Roma
skins.desc: Vittorio Veneto-class battleship – Roma.

skins.name: White Heron of Darkest Night
skins.desc: You seem to have known that I would be here. Then stay and spend the night with me. Just the two of us.

skins.name: Conte di Cavour
skins.desc: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Conte di Cavour.

skins.name: Fierce Beachside Battle
skins.desc: Commander, take this. Good, for the time being, you are a now a disciple under my command. It is time for us to mete out punishment to the unruly.

skins.name: Giulio Cesare
skins.desc: Conte di Cavour-class battleship – Giulio Cesare.

skins.name: Fitness Master
skins.desc: Both exercise and war are at their core about willpower! Now, get ready, Commander! We're not finished until you're dripping with sweat!

skins.name: High Tide Under the Sunlight
skins.desc: Tired already? For goodness' sake, I thought you'd be more reliable than this. Don't go burning all your energy at once, we still have a whole day of recreation ahead of us.

skins.name: Aquila
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier – Aquila.

skins.name: Sardegnian Shallows and Sunshine
skins.desc: Good day, my Commander. We have the day off to enjoy the sea breeze and the ocean waves~ Hehe, would you like to help yourself to some fruit?

skins.name: A Sip of Sardegnian Elegance
skins.desc: Oh, my Commander? I didn't expect to meet you here! Fortune smiles upon me today. Hehe~ If you have a minute to spare, would you care to join me for a cup of tea?

skins.name: Impero
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier – Impero.

skins.name: Languid Librarian
skins.desc: Seems school uniforms are all the hype. Veneto picked this one out for me. What are you dressed as, Commander? A teacher? A classmate?

skins.name: Torricelli
skins.desc: Brin-class submarine – Torricelli.

skins.name: Shady Seaside
skins.desc: Hehe, hehehehe... We have this little c-corner of the beach all to ourselves... Now, what should we do first... Hehehehe...

skins.name: Leonardo da Vinci
skins.desc: Marconi-class submarine – Leonardo da Vinci.

skins.name: Riverside Pirouette
skins.desc: Here to watch me rehearse just like these deer, Commander? Isn't it wonderful being surrounded by the beauty of nature? For a performance based on a fable such as this one, ambiance is key. Ehehe~♪

skins.name: Marco Polo
skins.desc: Battleship – Marco Polo.

skins.name: The Queen of Hearts
skins.desc: Me? Serve as your maid? Oho! That's more like it, Commander! How magnificent and ambitious of you! ...Only temporarily? And you're content with that?

skins.name: Grozny
skins.desc: Gnevny-class destroyer – Grozny.

skins.name: Bad Bunny Behind Bars
skins.desc: Comrade Commander, are you here to see my room? Hm? That Шутки isn't funny? Then how about... did my room come to see you, comrade Commander?

skins.name: Bunny Remodeling Plan?
skins.desc: Hmm... If I tweak Królik around a bit like this... But, it'll probably be a problem if I don't finish this in one go... Guess I'll think about it while I eat. Mhm.

skins.name: Shadowy Syndicate Showdown
skins.desc: Our shift starts now. Królik, Pirožkí, Manjuus – form up! Let us realize our Manjuu comrades' dreams!

skins.name: Tea Party with Królik
skins.desc: *burp*... Now I think I get the appeal of tea. Why is the cup so small, though? Do you have a bigger one on hand, Comrade Commander?

skins.name: Minsk
skins.desc: Leningrad-class destroyer – Minsk.

skins.name: Thunderous Jailor
skins.desc: You've violated the Minsk Protocol, comrade! Therefore, the sentence appropriate for you is imprisonment! Until when? Obviously, until your jailor is satisfied~♪

skins.name: Tashkent
skins.desc: Tashkent-class destroyer – Tashkent.

skins.name: The Bound Cruiser
skins.desc: ...*Sigh*, I never thought I'd get captured by these little guys... Dear comrade, does Tashkent really have to play along with this?

skins.name: The Blue Snoozer
skins.desc: Urrk... Who dares disturb Tashkent's slumber? ...Oh, it's you, dear comrade? Um, in that case... I can always get more rest later. Is something the matter?

skins.name: Tashkent μ
skins.desc: How do you like my outfit, dear comrade? ...Is that so? After all of Tashkent's work to become an idol, that's how you react? Hmph. Just you wait. My next concert will rock your socks off.

skins.name: The Bound Cruiser
skins.desc: ...*Sigh*, I never thought I'd get captured by these little guys... Dear comrade, does Tashkent really have to play along with this?

skins.name: The Blue Snoozer
skins.desc: Urrk... Who dares disturb Tashkent's slumber? ...Oh, it's you, dear comrade? Um, in that case... I can always get more rest later. Is something the matter?

skins.name: Stremitelny
skins.desc: Gnevny-class destroyer - Stremitelny

skins.name: No Snow No Life
skins.desc: It sucks not being able to play in the snow... Oh well! I'll play some games instead! Commander, let's play something fun together!

skins.name: Gremyashchy
skins.desc: Gnevny-class destroyer - Stremitelny

skins.name: A Daytime Delight is in a Book
skins.desc: Wh-who gave you the right to just barge in? ...I did? Huh. Well, seeing as you're here, I guess we could read a book together. Mm, that's all.

skins.name: Gromky
skins.desc: Gnevny-class destroyer—Gromky.

skins.name: Morning's Beckoning
skins.desc: Comrade! The morning is already here! Look how high the sun is in the sky!! C'mon, a wonderful day is calling to us~!!

skins.name: Soobrazitelny
skins.desc: Project 7U-class destroyer – Soobrazitelny

skins.name: The Machinery of Life
skins.desc: Yes, these data and results are quite interesting... Though they mean nothing to me! I am a genius mechanic, not an analyst! Ahh-ha-ha-haah!

skins.name: Kiev
skins.desc: Project 48-class destroyer – Kiev

skins.name: Backstreet Silver Sonata
skins.desc: Seeing you here puts me at ease. I know this stakeout will go smoothly as long as you're here. Mhm, all is fine.

skins.name: Avrora
skins.desc: Pallada-class Light Cruiser, Avrora

skins.name: Shackled Saule
skins.desc: "I am Avrora, the princess bound within this tower by a cruel fate... My beloved, please come for me soon..."

skins.name: Not Cut Out For This?
skins.desc: "Muahaha... Now, these streets belong to me..." Sorry, I bit my tongue... Hmm, getting into this role is quite difficult for me after all.

skins.name: Pamiat' Merkuria
skins.desc: Bogatyr-class protected cruiser – Pamiat Merkuria.

skins.name: Caged Minx
skins.desc: What kinda exercise is this?! Nobody said I'd become a dang showpiece! Come on, get this thing off me, NOW!

skins.name: Sweet Cherry Memories
skins.desc: Mmmh~ I sure could get used to this life~ Oh, Commander, thanks for being my gofer~♪ Ah, you can leave the cherries right over here!

skins.name: Chic and Cheeky
skins.desc: Aaand send DM to Rossiya... Finally you showed up, Commander! So, where are you taking me, hmm?

skins.name: Mercurial Chocolate Love
skins.desc: Happy Valentine's Day~♪ Did you come here to enjoy my chocolate? Then, try guessing where I hid my chocolate – if you get it right, I'll give it to you~♪ Is it here... or maybe over here? Ahahaha~♡

skins.name: Pamiat' Merkuria (Retrofit)
skins.desc: My retrofitting is done! Look forward to seeing how both my cuteness and combat potential have been upgraded!

skins.name: Chapayev
skins.desc: Chapayev-class cruiser – Chapayev.

skins.name: The Captive Cavalier
skins.desc: Commander, what's going on? Did I... do something wrong...? This was all just... meant to be an exercise, right?

skins.name: White Cavalier's Respite
skins.desc: Phew... Oh my, Commander, I'm sorry I didn't welcome you at the door. You don't have to be so tense - I already know not to try doing anything weird with you. Hehe~

skins.name: Indigo & Lantern-Lit Summer Night
skins.desc: You've been looking for me? Heehee, sorry if I made you worry, I just had to feel the night breeze in my hair for a bit. Why don't you stay and enjoy it with me?

skins.name: Kirov
skins.desc: Kirov-Class cruiser—Kirov

skins.name: Blend R
skins.desc: Comrade Commander, you've come at a good time. I've recently taken a liking to this blend of coffee. Want some as well? No need to be shy.

skins.name: Drifting Justice
skins.desc: Halt! You have nowhere left to run!! ...Well done, Comrade Commander, what a thrilling chase we had on our hands! What, you think I'm well-suited for this job? You tease too much, bahaha!

skins.name: High Jump Star
skins.desc: ...Hmph! Just short of a new personal best, huh? But make no mistake, Comrade Commander. Keep watching me and your patience WILL be rewarded with a breathtaking record!

skins.name: Kuybyshev
skins.desc: Chapayev-class light cruiser – Kuybyshev.

skins.name: Maestro of Sterling Strings
skins.desc: ...Thus marks the end of this tune. The Dragon Empery has graciously allowed me to perform in their Spring Festival celebration. Are you here to listen, Commander? In that case... How did you like the song? Heehee.

skins.name: Murmansk
skins.desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Murmansk

skins.name: Sceneries of Pure Snow
skins.desc: ...Achoo! Uhh, good morning... Snow? Yeah, it is snowing today... Woah, it's really coming down hard... Ahaha~

skins.name: Tallinn
skins.desc: Heavy cruiser - Tallinn.

skins.name: Nostalgic Pilsner
skins.desc: What, you've never seen the inside of a shipgirl's room? It's not like you're here on official business, so stop standing around already. Find a place to sit and relax.

skins.name: As You Say, Ma'am!
skins.desc: You've reached the Bureau of Investigation... Oh boy, another case. Commander, finish up your paperwork ASAP. We've got witnesses to interview.

skins.name: Gangut
skins.desc: Gangut-class battleship – Gangut.

skins.name: Imposing Warden
skins.desc: You have my thanks for this exercise, comrade! I shall gladly carry out the important duty of judge, jury, and rehabilitator!

skins.name: Keeper of the Firewater
skins.desc: ...Bwahaah! I've had all kinds of liquor, but nothing beats the stuff back home! Comrade, let's have a toast to the coming off-duty days!

skins.name: Sovetskaya Belorussiya
skins.desc: Sovestsky Soyuz-class battleship - Sovetskaya Belorussiya.

skins.name: Relaxation Stratagem
skins.desc: To pass the time by proactively reading, or by passively enjoying the company of others... Ah, good morning, Comrade, I've been expecting you. Hahaha!

skins.name: Sovetskaya Rossiya
skins.desc: Sovetsky Soyuz-class battleship – Sovetskaya Rossiya.

skins.name: The Lackadaisical Lookout
skins.desc: "Situation normal in all sectors of the facility..." Oh, it is you. I was just giving Minsk the daily report. Do you have something?

skins.name: Arkhangelsk
skins.desc: R-class battleship – Arkhangelsk

skins.name: Grandiose Getaway
skins.desc: Your choice treasure now belongs to master thief Arkhangelsk! Think you can arrest me? Then stop gawking and come get me!

skins.name: Volga
skins.desc: Project 72-class aircraft carrier – Volga

skins.name: An Irresistible AR Adventure
skins.desc: Volga here. I'm currently tracking an important witness. *gurgle* ...Is my stomach rumbling because this AR game requires so much stamina? Ugh, lost track of the witness just now...

skins.name: Kronshtadt
skins.desc: Project 69-class cruiser – Kronshtadt

skins.name: Begin the Rush!
skins.desc: Listen up, assholes! We have you surrounded! I'm Kronshtadt, squad leader of the Northern Parliament Special Forces! You have only one option: come out with your hands in the air and surrender!

skins.name: Chkalov
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier - Chkalov.

skins.name: Seaside Sunset
skins.desc: Oh? What made you come over here instead of heading down to the beach? Surely you didn't ditch your friends on a hard-earned day off just to see me? But, I don't mind. It's called a day off because you get to decide how to spend your time.

skins.name: Le Triomphant
skins.desc: Le Fantasque-class destroyer – Le Triomphant.

skins.name: Forbin
skins.desc: L'Adroit-class destroyer – Forbin.

skins.name: Fleur Blanche
skins.desc: It's good to be able to stop and smell the roses every now and then. Um, Commander, would you be able to accompany me a bit longer?

skins.name: École de Chevalier
skins.desc: Even though I'm an Iris Libre squire, I'm currently working hard to have a rich student life. Um... maybe this is a bit too laid back?

skins.name: Feast of Champagne
skins.desc: Good evening, Commander. I am currently enjoying the party in the company of my friends, as my duties as a squire entail. Um... I've had a bit too much to drink? R-really...?

skins.name: Fleur de Mariée
skins.desc: At long last, this wonderful day is here. It feels like I'm dreaming... I'm so happy, I just... Forgive me, I promised myself I wouldn't cry... I, Forbin the squire, shall remain by your side for the rest of my life!

skins.name: Forbin (Retrofit)
skins.desc: My hard work has finally paid off! Commander, thank you for your guidance all this time! I'll return the favor by bringing you even more honors in battle!

skins.name: Le Téméraire
skins.desc: Le Hardi-class destroyer – Le Téméraire.

skins.name: Summery Temeraire!
skins.desc: Commander, I've finished changing into my swimsuit! Heheh~ let's head down to the beach and enjoy ourselves as much as we can!

skins.name: Dreamy Dolce
skins.desc: How do I look? These pajamas are super cute, aren't they? Ehehe, I really like this one! It even matches with Opiniâtre's!

skins.name: L'Opiniâtre
skins.desc: Le Hardi-class destroyer – L'Opiniâtre.

skins.name: Beachside Magician
skins.desc: It is said that the summertime sea holds an extraordinary enchantment over people... but the only supernatural thing I'm feeling is this accursed heat... Am I missing something?

skins.name: Le Terrible
skins.desc: Le Fantasque-class large destroyer - Le Terrible.

skins.name: Silence, Slumber, and Solace
skins.desc: Zzz... Commander...? Sorry... for showing you this unsightly side of mine... I'm just, not a morning person... Zzzzz...

skins.name: Sunlight, Seaspray, and Sanctity
skins.desc: How goes your day, Commander? Hehe, are you looking for my clever sister, Le Malin? If so, you would do well to search somewhere less... popular~♪

skins.name: Maillé Brézé
skins.desc: Vauquelin-class destroyer – Maillé Brézé.

skins.name: The Noble Knight's Last Stand
skins.desc: H-h-halt, intruder! Thou art intruding in the domain of an Iris Libre Templar Knight, a crime punishable by... Eek! I'm begging you, spare my life! ...It's you, Lord Commander?!

skins.name: Sugary Sabbatical
skins.desc: Enjoying sweet pastries in a lovely dress – heehee, such bliss! ...I care not how unbecoming this is of a knight! I saved these desserts for my holiday! Let me enjoy myself, would you!

skins.name: Émile Bertin
skins.desc: Light cruiser – Émile Bertin.

skins.name: Côte d'Azur
skins.desc: Commander, does my swimsuit pique your fancy? I'm actually quite proud of my fashion sense. *Giggle* Now, let's enjoy midsummer together~

skins.name: Maid Fantastique
skins.desc: I heard of this romantic concept of maid outfits, and thought I'd try one on to see how it feels~ What are your thoughts, Commander?

skins.name: Gilded Dance
skins.desc: Modest though it may be, isn't this a lovely little garden? Come, Commander! Let us dance surrounded by Mother Nature~

skins.name: Émile Bertin (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Émile Bertin, retrofit complete! I feel like a completely new person! To show my gratitude, Commander, I'll perform a brand new dance for you!

skins.name: Jeanne d'Arc
skins.desc: Light cruiser – Jeanne d'Arc.

skins.name: Saintess of the Sea
skins.desc: "O chosen hero, I bestow this sword upon you so that you may clear any obstacles in your path..." Commander, how did that sound?

skins.name: Richelieu
skins.desc: Richelieu-class battleship – Richelieu.

skins.name: Fleuron of the Waves
skins.desc: This swimsuit... Yes, the one Émile picked out for me, seems a bit skimpy... I didn't think she'd be the type to trick me into wearing something like this, but... Commander, where are you looking?

skins.name: Evergreen Prophecy
skins.desc: Commander, I wish you a Happy New Year. May you avail yourself of the period of repose that follows the culmination of the year's duties. I pray that you and everyone else may receive the blessing of the Heavens.

skins.name: Béarn
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier – Béarn.

skins.name: Summer Lifeguard
skins.desc: Are you perhaps feeling unwell, Commander? Oh, I see, you're just looking for a shaded place to rest? Acknowledged. In that case, you may sit here if you'd like.

skins.name: Surcouf
skins.desc: Cruiser submarine – Surcouf.

skins.name: Shopping Time!
skins.desc: Hmm? Commander, are you shopping as well? If so, why don't you come along and take a look around? ... Huh? Of course you can't climb on. That'd be illegal.

skins.name: Loisirs Balnéaires
skins.desc: Mmmh~ Bonjour, Commander~ Nothing feels better than the waves lapping at your skin~ Oh, Commander, why don't you come lie down and experience it for yourself?

skins.name: Saint Louis
skins.desc: Heavy cruiser – Saint Louis.

skins.name: Holy Knight's Resplendence
skins.desc: With all due respect, Commander, this finery and this throne are not fit for one such as myself. Despite the hallowed name I have inherited, I am nothing more than a warrior. —However, if such an arrangement pleases you, then I shall hold my objections.

skins.name: Alluring Administrator
skins.desc: Commander, regarding your next appointment... Ah, hard work is one of the highest virtues of the Iris's holy knights. On weekdays or vacations, in knights' armor or the Dragon Empery's attire, there can be no pause to my prayer, my training, or my duties as the administrator of your will.

skins.name: Champagne
skins.desc: Battleship – Champagne.

skins.name: Lapis Lazuli's First Dream
skins.desc: It is not against the teachings to halt one's pursuit of destiny and to surrender to the warm draft of festivities. It is mankind's prerogative to seek out auspicious portents.

skins.name: Brest
skins.desc: Large cruiser - Brest.

skins.name: Marine Muse
skins.desc: "I devote this paean to thee, Champion of seas blue and free." There, the song is completed. But we've come all this way... Shall we continue our adventure through these undersea ruins, Champion?

skins.name: Le Mars
skins.desc: L'Adroit-class destroyer – Le Mars.

skins.name: Été Brillant
skins.desc: It's summer~! Summer is here, Commander! Let's head down to the beach to play! I'll show you why I'm feared in water gun fights!

skins.name: Écolière Heureuse
skins.desc: Hey! Over here! Hehe. I didn't expect to run into you at school, Commander. What are you doing here?

skins.name: Splendorous Debut
skins.desc: Commander, thanks for coming to pick me up! I don't often get the chance to wear formal clothes, though it is a little hard to move around... Oh, but I can deal with it!

skins.name: Le Mars (Retrofit)
skins.desc: Retro~ fit~ com~ plete! The new and improved Le Mars is at your service~!

skins.name: Tartu
skins.desc: Vauquelin-class destroyer – Tartu.

skins.name: Overthinking Summer
skins.desc: Commander, you're not going to get into the water? ...Ah, I'm fine right here. To tell you the truth, I once got washed away by the waves, and then got laughed at by Vauquelin... so I'm perfectly fine right here.

skins.name: Vauquelin
skins.desc: Vauquelin-class destroyer – Vauquelin.

skins.name: Innocent Summer Knight
skins.desc: Commandeeer! What are you doing? It's our day off! Turn the work part of your brain off and just have fun! C'mon, let's enjoy ourselves on the beach!

skins.name: One-Girl Orchestra
skins.desc: Yes, the strings... I can hear the celebratory melody... Now, follow my lead and we'll take this song to greater– Oh, Commander? What's all this, you ask? Uhh... You know... Ahahaha...

skins.name: Le Malin
skins.desc: Le Fantasque-class destroyer – Le Malin.

skins.name: Sleepy Sunday
skins.desc: Morning, Commander~ Mm, the Sabbath is the day of rest, so I shall not budge from my sacred charge even if you were to call Triomphant over. I solemnly swear to do absolutely nothing today.

skins.name: Mercredi at the Secret Base
skins.desc: I must commend you for being able to find my secret base, Commander... but unfortunately for you, I refuse to return to the office today. Just... *yawn*...let me spend the whole day sleeping here...

skins.name: Listless Lapin
skins.desc: Zzz... zzz... Huh? Commander? I was in the middle of a nap... Oh, this outfit? It's cool, comfy, and cute. If you don't need anything from me, I'm going back to sleep...

skins.name: Le Malin μ
skins.desc: I am the Iris's shining sword, Le Malin. As the shimmering idol who chases the waves, may your souls be healed by my songs of prayer.

skins.name: Sleepy Sunday
skins.desc: Morning, Commander~ Mm, the Sabbath is the day of rest, so I shall not budge from my sacred charge even if you were to call Triomphant over. I solemnly swear to do absolutely nothing today.

skins.name: Mercredi at the Secret Base
skins.desc: I must commend you for being able to find my secret base, Commander... but unfortunately for you, I refuse to return to the office today. Just... *yawn*...let me spend the whole day sleeping here...

skins.name: Listless Lapin
skins.desc: Zzz... zzz... Huh? Commander? I was in the middle of a nap... Oh, this outfit? It's cool, comfy, and cute. If you don't need anything from me, I'm going back to sleep...

skins.name: L'Indomptable
skins.desc: Le Fantasque-class destroyer – L'Indomptable.

skins.name: Little Red Riding Hood's Worries
skins.desc: What a farce, making a proud Templar Knight portray a helpless little girl... Why am I lying here, you ask? Hmph. Because Le Malin asserted this is the best way to get in touch with my "vulnerable side"...

skins.name: Temp in Low Temperatures
skins.desc: Hmm... Traveling by foot from here would be quickest. Ah... It's snowing. Hmph! A little snow and wind can scarcely faze a noble Templar Knight! I'll be back shortly!

skins.name: La Galissonnière
skins.desc: La Galissonnière-class light cruiser – La Galissonnière.

skins.name: Pristine Piscene
skins.desc: Summertime means pool time! Oh, hey, Commander. What are you waiting for? Come over and let's have fun!

skins.name: Lush Spring Dreams
skins.desc: Happy New Year, again! So, you wanna try sharing this "cross-cupped wine?" What, it's not a drinking game? Welp, I guess I've still got a whole ton to learn about the Dragon Empery's customs~

skins.name: Black Cat of All Hallows' Eve
skins.desc: If you ignore me, I'll use my black cat magic to turn you into a pumpkin! Is that Halloweeny enough? Ahahaha! I'm just messing! C'mon, let's go do somethin' fun tonight, Commander!

skins.name: Foch
skins.desc: Suffren-class Heavy Cruiser—Foch

skins.name: Rainbow Rendezvous
skins.desc: Yo, Commander, did I keep you waiting? Sorry 'bout that. You know how it goes, sometimes it's really hard for a girl to pick out the right thing to wear. Anyway, let's get going~♪

skins.name: Algérie
skins.desc: Algérie-class heavy cruiser – Algérie.

skins.name: White Sand Paradise
skins.desc: Oh my, hehe... Are you enjoying the warmth of the sunlight here? I'm glad that you're finding some time to relax here, but wouldn't you rather come play with everyone else?

skins.name: Red Queen's Decree
skins.desc: Oh my, it seems that the one who ended up coming wasn't little Alice, but you instead... Do you plan to defy me as well, Commander? If so, I'll have to put you on trial for your sins... How was my acting just now? Hehe~

skins.name: Dunkerque
skins.desc: Dunkerque-class battlecruiser – Dunkerque.

skins.name: Summer Sucré
skins.desc: I've been waiting so long for summer... and it's so worth it - the sun, the sand, the waves, and everyone's laughter. Commander, why don't we take this opportunity to enjoy some crullers together?

skins.name: Afternoon Venus
skins.desc: Don't you simply adore the atmosphere in this place? It's one of my favorites. The desserts here are to die for. Would you like a taste?

skins.name: Jean Bart
skins.desc: Richelieu-class battleship – Jean Bart.

skins.name: Uninhibited Bloodstone
skins.desc: The guest of honor shouldn't be wandering around looking for girls drinking alone... Hmph, might as well have a drink while you're here anyway.

skins.name: Private Après Midi
skins.desc: You damn scalawag... You don't just sneak into someone's hideaway without consequences, ya know. Though, I found this place by pure chance too. Don't go tellin' anyone else about it!

skins.name: First Snow Upon the Cutlass's Edge
skins.desc: Bonne année... Or rather, I should say "Happy New Year" here, yes? A year of peace and prosperity passes, and we are here to welcome another... and I must thank you for making that possible.

skins.name: Gascogne μ
skins.desc: Gascogne module change process complete. New directive: sing for the world. Master's order is my will.

skins.name: Tropical Environs Acclimation Service Equipment
skins.desc: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Requesting detailed instructions for how to "have fun on the beach."

skins.name: Joffre
skins.desc: Joffre-class aircraft carrier – Joffre.

skins.name: Ensorcelled Snow White
skins.desc: Were you planning on freeing me from this spell? Then I suppose you're prepared to lock lips with me. Even though I'm already awake, um... that's just part of the ritual.

skins.name: Gascogne
skins.desc: Battleship – Gascogne.

skins.name: Tropical Environs Acclimation Service Equipment
skins.desc: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Requesting detailed instructions for how to "have fun on the beach."

skins.name: Royal Fortune
skins.desc: Pirate sailing frigate – Royal Fortune.

skins.name: Treats from the Deep
skins.desc: Tonight's dessert is not a cake or a pastry... What are you looking around for? YOU'RE my dessert! Heheh, scared you, didn't I?

skins.name: Hunter META
skins.desc: Greetings, Commander. I'm Hunter. I hunt, as you might've surmised. Is this place... my new base?

skins.name: Fortune META
skins.desc: Well met, Commander. My name is Fortune. Please don't worry about these ch-chains... They're there to... keep my power in check.

skins.name: Helena META
skins.desc: Were you looking for me? I am willing to lend you my power – provided that you promise not to hide anything from me.

skins.name: Memphis META
skins.desc: I'm Memphis. You may not know me, but I know you and I know you well. Don't you worry, I'm not a threat – you can trust me. Today I assume the role of your right hand and bodyguard.

skins.name: Sheffield META
skins.desc: So you're the Commander... in other words, my Master. Alright, got it. The name's Sheffield, and the game's pointing my gun at vermin – Ah, please disregard that little gesture I made just now.

skins.name: Trento META
skins.desc: I am heavy cruiser Trento, and I will be your assistant. The best thing I could ask for is that my support helps you achieve your goals.

skins.name: Gneisenau META
skins.desc: You're... the Commander, right? In other words, the one with the authority to control me. Though I have no interest in you as an individual, I will still obey your orders... At least for the time being.

skins.name: Scharnhorst META
skins.desc: I'm Iron Blood battlecruiser Scharnhorst. I am keen to join forces with a Commander as talented as you. Don't let my expectations of you be misplaced.

skins.name: Repulse META
skins.desc: I'm Repulse, Renown-class battlecruiser. I've been through a lot... but that's in the past. Now, I'm a part of this port. Whenever you're in a pinch, come see me.

skins.name: Renown META
skins.desc: Salutations to you, Commander. I am battlecruiser Renown. I hope that this battle-worn blade can become your power.

skins.name: Fusou META
skins.desc: I am battleship Fusou. I have come to bring peace to this world's tormented souls. Commander, do you seek blessings... or redemption?

skins.name: Yamashiro META
skins.desc: Are you this fleet's Commander, Milord? I see. You have great potential, but your skills need some refinement. I wonder what's the best way to train you... You'll see soon enough – stay alert until then!

skins.name: Arizona META
skins.desc: I am Arizona... This may be improper of me, but is it really alright for me to stay here? ...Very well, Commander. If that is what you've decided...

skins.name: Queen Elizabeth META
skins.desc: So you are the Commander? Very well. From this point forth, you will use your courage and intellect for our purposes! ...We don't have all day, now. You are our servant, so this won't go anywhere until you swear your fealty.

skins.name: Hiyou META
skins.desc: Ahahahaha! The fact that you've chosen me means you clearly have a discerning eye. So, what now? Where's the enemy you need me to sink?

skins.name: Junyou META
skins.desc: I'm... Junyou. Please give me your orders... Commander.

skins.name: Hiryuu META
skins.desc: I'm getting all fired up! The name's Hiryuu, Hiryuu from the 2nd CarDiv. As a member of this fleet, I'll obey your orders. I do hope that you are qualified to lead us.

skins.name: Ark Royal META
skins.desc: Aircraft carrier Ark Royal, at your service. I hereby vow to lend you my strength for as long as you harbour honourable ambitions!

skins.name: Souryuu META
skins.desc: I am Souryuu of the Sakura Empire's 2nd CarDiv. Let's skip the formalities and get to work right away.

skins.name: Neptune
skins.desc: Heya! My name's Neptune! Nice to meet you!

skins.name: Noire
skins.desc: Are you the commander? Hmm... Very well. I'm Noire. The CPU of Lastation. You can put your mind at ease now that I'm here.

skins.name: Blanc
skins.desc: I'm Blanc. Nice to meet you. Maybe you could introduce some intriguing books from this world to me...

skins.name: Vert
skins.desc: My name is Vert, I am the CPU of Leanbox. I'm very good at first-person shooters, so please let me handle all combat-related matters!

skins.name: Purple Heart
skins.desc: I am Purple Heart, the CPU of Planeptune. And you must be the commander. I will follow your orders from now.

skins.name: Goddesses' Promise
skins.desc: Oh, Commander? Won't you join me in a short conversation? I'll tell you things about Planeptune. Oh, and I'm eagerly awaiting the day you come to Planeptune for a visit.

skins.name: Black Heart
skins.desc: I'm the CPU of Lastation, Black Heart. I've rushed here all the way from Gamindustri to lend you my aid. Be grateful.

skins.name: Goddesses' Smile
skins.desc: It's good to take it easy and celebrate once in a while, but especially in moments like these, you can't afford to let your guard down. Commander, why don't we spar for a bit? Don't even think about holding back - come at me!

skins.name: White Heart
skins.desc: I'm White Heart, the guardian CPU of Lowee. Pleased to meet you. I'm gonna give you a taste of a CPU's power!

skins.name: Goddesses' Humility
skins.desc: B-bastard! Where are you looking? I bet you're thinking I look like a kid! Eh....? They're just right? If Commander says something like that... I don't know how to react...

skins.name: Green Heart
skins.desc: I am the CPU of Leanbox, Green Heart. No matter who the enemy is, I will not hold back. Are you ready?

skins.name: Goddesses' Moment
skins.desc: Commander, are you having a good time? Ehehe, I certainly am. It's not often that we get to relax like this. Why don't we head out and enjoy the breeze?

skins.name: Kizuna AI
skins.desc: HAI DOMO! Kizuna AI here! Are you the commander I've heard rumors about? It's a pleasure to meet and work with you!

skins.name: Festive Kizuna AI
skins.desc: The clothes from the Sakura Empire are so stylish! Commander, since it's a rare occasion, let's go take a look around! Ah, of course, don't forget to run the reel~♪

skins.name: Elegant Kizuna AI
skins.desc: Well met. I'm Kizuna AI, the new addition to your base. I will do all in my power to be at least of some use. It is a pleasure meeting you, Commander.

skins.name: Anniversary Kizuna AI
skins.desc: Kizuna AI here, wearing a dress, coming at you! Be it concert or combat, I'll give it my all!

skins.name: Super Gamer Kizuna AI
skins.desc: HAI DOMO! Virtual Gamer Kizuna AI here! Don't worry, Commander, I've played AL a whole bunch before! ... Wait, I've become a ship now?!

skins.name: Shirakami Fubuki
skins.desc: We meet at last! I'm Hololive's virtual fox, Shirakami Fubuki! Commander, now that you've called me, we're gonna have a foxin' good time! Now then, let's get to work!

skins.name: Beachside Fox
skins.desc: Tada~! It's your favorite Shirakami Fubuki, Hololive Summer version! Commander, pleased to be your fox!

skins.name: Tokino Sora
skins.desc: Hey Commander, it's nice to meet you~! I'm Tokino Sora, a virtual idol affiliated with Hololive! I'll do my absolute best here like I always do! I'll be in your care, so cheer me on, Commander!

skins.name: Under the Clear Sky
skins.desc: "Hello, my friends! I hope you're well~! This is Sora, on site at a beach in a slightly different world!" Beach visits just feel so invigorating, don't they? On another note, I can't swim…

skins.name: Minato Aqua
skins.desc: G-Good Aquafternoon...! I'm Minato Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive~ U-Ugh... I didn't know I would have to introduce myself in this outfit!

skins.name: Marine Maid
skins.desc: Commander, good Aquafternoon~! Nice to meet you, it's Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive! I'll show ya what the strongest maid can do!

skins.name: Natsuiro Matsuri
skins.desc: I'm the lovely high school girl affiliated with Hololive, Natsuiro Matsuri!! I love singing and having all kinds of lively conversations with people, so make sure to keep your eyes on me!

skins.name: Matsuri's Day Off
skins.desc: I'm the lovely high school girl, now in her extra-pure pajamas, Natsuiro Matsuri! Hey hey, Commander, what do you think? Surprised? Don't gawk at me too much~

skins.name: Nakiri Ayame
skins.desc: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri! Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon! Ay have come from the great beyond with my accompanying spirits!

skins.name: Summertime Nakiri
skins.desc: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri~! Ay am not used to this outfit and am a little embarrassed... But Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon!

skins.name: Murasaki Shion
skins.desc: I am the mastermind magician, Murasaki Shion! Come and be bewitched by my mature, seductive outfit!

skins.name: Virtual Magician
skins.desc: Here comes Murasaki Shion, Hololive's famous virtual magician! This world will bear witness to my brilliance!

skins.name: Ookami Mio
skins.desc: Good Miovening! I'm Ookami Mio. Over here, I seem to be... some sort of aircraft carrier. Let's get along well.

skins.name: Summer Vacation
skins.desc: I changed into my swimsuit, but I wonder if it looks right on me? An outfit like this might make you feel breezier just by looking at it~

skins.name: Marie Rose
skins.desc: Hello! Oh... What am I supposed to call you? "Commander"? Got it! My name is Marie Rose. Just call me Marie, okay? I'm counting on your support, Commander!

skins.name: Devilish Servant Against the Splashing Waves
skins.desc: Hmm, this swimsuit is pretty cute, but isn't it a bit childish? ...In any case, if you like it, then it's all good!

skins.name: Honoka
skins.desc: Um... Are you the Commander? Oh, perfect! It's nice to meet you. My name is Honoka! I don't know how much I'll be able to help, but... let's be friends!

skins.name: Summer Angel on the Shore
skins.desc: Whoa, the sea is so pretty~! It's as beautiful as the Venus Islands! I'm so blown away, I don't even feel the heat anymore!

skins.name: Kasumi
skins.desc: Are you the Owner of the port? The "Commander"? Hello. My name is Kasumi, I'll be staying here for the foreseeable future. I hope we can both get along on friendly terms.

skins.name: Springside Mist
skins.desc: I was amazed to see the port had such a scenic place as this... Truly, you can't go without taking this view in. Right, Commander?

skins.name: Misaki
skins.desc: It's nice to meet you! From what I've heard, you're the "Commander," right? I'm Misaki. I have experience with various part-time jobs, so... I'm confident that I can be of help to you all. Let's do our best!

skins.name: Golden Photoshoot
skins.desc: A photoshoot? That'd be similar to what I did before coming here, but... um, this swimsuit is a bit much... Commander, is this what you're into? Geez... It's so embarrassing...

skins.name: Nagisa
skins.desc: Are you the person who led Misaki to this port? You go by the name... "Commander"? Hmm... I don't know how you sweet-talked her into it, but you're not fooling me. The moment you do anything strange... you better be on guard! My name? It's Nagisa. You... silly dog!

skins.name: Blue Skies, Good Vibes
skins.desc: Whew! The wind feels great! ...What are you staring at me like that for, you silly dog? You're the one who said you wanted to go to the beach, remember? To start with, how about... we take a stroll?

skins.name: Nyotengu
skins.desc: Oh? You don't seem to fear me... Who might you be? ...I see, so it is you who rules over this place. Then I shall call you "Commander." I am Nyotengu. You would do best to keep me entertained, hehe.

skins.name: Scarlet-Tinged Hot Spring Vacation
skins.desc: Oho! To think there was a place with this much class... Not bad! I shall hereby be enjoying my hot springs vacation right here, hehehe.

skins.name: Monica
skins.desc: Are you the one in charge here? The "Commander"? I'm Monica, the dealer! Well, dealer-in-training. I know it's sudden, but would you care to gamble with me? The stakes will, of course, be high!

skins.name: The Ace of Hearts
skins.desc: "Welcome to Monica's Fantabulous Casino! Where you can have your every whim satisfied!" ...Oh, that doesn't sound very casino-managery? Heheh!

skins.name: Haruka Amami
skins.desc: Hello, Commander! I'm the idol, Haruka Amami! I'll do my best to share my dreams with everyone in port! Let's all have a great time together!

skins.name: A Taste of Tranquility
skins.desc: Good evening, Commander! Are you also taking a break? If so, let's go get some candied apples and have a little chat~♪

skins.name: Chihaya Kisaragi
skins.desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Chihaya Kisaragi. Are you the one in charge of this port? I look forward to working with you.

skins.name: Reflections of Heavenly Flowers
skins.desc: Oh, the fireworks display is starting. I'm planning to meet up with the others after this, but... Why don't we spend some time enjoying the view here first?

skins.name: Iori Minase
skins.desc: Hello, hello~! My name is Iori Minase! It's such a pleasure to meet you! ...Huh? There's no need for me to force myself...? Hey, wait a second, what do you mean by that?!

skins.name: A Little Evening Secret
skins.desc: Blowing bubbles while sitting on a swing... It might seem a bit childish, but there's nothing wrong with enjoying activities like these every so often.

skins.name: Azusa Miura
skins.desc: Why hello, my name's Azusa Miura~ Um, this is a port, right? And these are... shipgirls? Um~ Where exactly am I?

skins.name: Midsummer Relaxation
skins.desc: Listening to the wind flow through the chimes on the porch seems to carry the summer heat right away. Commander, would you also like to come unwind with me?

skins.name: Ritsuko Akizuki
skins.desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Ritsuko Akizuki. I was wondering what was going to happen to me when I suddenly got blown away, but... In any case, I'm pleased to make your acquaintance!

skins.name: Paddle Showdown - Summer Formation
skins.desc: Sorry, what? A paddle showdown? Commander, please... You play that in a kimono, not a yutaka. But if you insist... If I win, you're buying me an ice cream!

skins.name: Ami Futami
skins.desc: Nihihi! I'm the idol, Ami Futami! This place seems awfully lively, just perfect for pranking~! See you around, Commander!

skins.name: Summer Flowers and Sizzling Beats
skins.desc: Summer's all about the festivals, and Ami Futami's the queen of festivals! Even the fireworks soaring through the sky can't hold a candle to how brilliant Ami is, so keep your eyes on me, Commander~♪

skins.name: Mami Futami
skins.desc: Nihihi~♪ I'm the idol, Mami Futami! You'll get to feast your eyes on how alluring Mami is, so look forward to it, Commander~!

skins.name: Alluring Festival
skins.desc: Woah~! They're starting to send up the huge fireworks! ...Hey, Commander, just where are you looking? Did Mami's alluring yukata make you go crazy with desire~?

skins.name: Rikka Takarada
skins.desc: Um, my name is Rikka Takarada. I'm still a bit confused about what's going on, but... I guess for the time being, I'm in good hands.

skins.name: Blue Sky Station
skins.desc: The train still isn't here yet? ...Oh, what a coincidence to see you here, Commander. Where were you headed?

skins.name: Akane Shinjo
skins.desc: Hey there, the name's Akane Shinjo. This rigging looks super cool, like it's right out of a mecha. Now if only there were some kaiju around, that'd be the best...

skins.name: A Vacation Just for Two
skins.desc: Welcome back, Commander. You sure brought a lot of goodies back for me, huh? Now then, don't just keep standing there, hurry and come to me~

skins.name: Hass
skins.desc: Hello, I'm Hass. I was suddenly blown away to this strange place... But, I guess it seems interesting enough here. By the way, is it okay to shoot some videos here?

skins.name: Seaside Scoop!
skins.desc: Hass here. Tonight, we're going to take a walk around the port at night. Aaaand, we even have a special guest– the Commander! ...Psst, hey, look at the camera real quick!

skins.name: Namiko
skins.desc: Heyyo, it's Namiko! Uhh, wait, is this that whole getting-reincarnated-in-another-world thing that's been super popular? ...It's not, huh. Well, in any case, nice to meet you!

skins.name: Miss Street-Wise
skins.desc: Woo, you're here! So, how was it? This meeting spot was pretty easy to find, right? Welp, let's get going then!

skins.name: Yume Minami
skins.desc: Hello, my name is Yume Minami. I've ended up in this world for whatever reason. I'll do my best to contribute to the fleet as a heavy cruiser.

skins.name: A Dream Upon an Open Windowsill
skins.desc: How lovely. From here, you can see across the entire port, as well as the shimmering ocean... Oh, Commander, here to enjoy the view with me?

skins.name: Chise Asukagawa
skins.desc: Woahhh, I somehow ended up in a totally unknown place... Oh, um, my name's Chise Asukagawa! Since I might be here for a while, thanks for looking after me!

skins.name: Together, Swimming through the Sky
skins.desc: Woaah, the sun's coming out! It feels so great outside after the rain... Oh, Commander! Let's take a stroll through the sky together!

skins.name: Mujina
skins.desc: Kaiju Eugenicist, Mujina. I suppose I'm a battleship now. Just asking to be sure... There are no kaiju in your world, correct?

skins.name: Golden Promenade
skins.desc: You've come as well, Commander? In that case, let's accompany each other back while watching the gingko leaves fall.

skins.name: Late-Night Alchemist
skins.desc: Hey there, Commander! Hehe, it's been a long while since I had a sleepover with someone. You know, I've really been looking forward to today. So, what would you like to do first?

skins.name: Bedtime Memories
skins.desc: Hehe, today was such a fun day... Oh, good evening, Commander. I was just writing my diary entry for the day. Since you're here, why don't you help me out?

skins.name: Rest Betwixt Dreams and Reality
skins.desc: Phew, that's everything taken care of for the day... Huh?! Commander, how long have you been there?! I-I apologize for letting you see my slovenly side... Please, just come over here for now.

skins.name: Moonlit Encounter
skins.desc: You shouldn't be up this late. What, you can't sleep? You want to stay up with me? ...Fine, I'll keep you company. I haven't been able to get a wink of sleep anyway.

skins.name: Fairy Dreamer Beneath the Starry Sky
skins.desc: An elegant verdure, a pellucid azure. I never knew there was such a lovely place at this port... Oh Commander, are you also out on a nighttime stroll?
